programme.title: Även anglar ater bonor
programme.desc: Fribrottaren Charlie (Bud Spencer) och drommaren Sonny (Giuliano Gemma) ar två fattiga tuffingar i 30-talets Chicago som hoppas på battre tider. De får chansen till stora pengar nar de borjar arbeta for en maffiaboss. Problemet ar att de ar alldeles for blodiga. De lånar ut pengar till fattiga istallet for att inkassera beskyddarpengar och driver hela tiden maffiabossen till vansinne. Till slut beslutar sig skurkarna for att undanroja Charlie och Sonny. Men de har glomt en sak - Charlies formidabla styrka sitter framst i navarna!

programme.title: Blue Steel
programme.desc: For en nyexaminerad polis finns det en sak som ar farligare an att visa upp en mordares fantasi. Att bli den.

programme.title: Saints and Soldiers: Airborne Creed
programme.desc: Den 15 augusti 1944 hoppar en pluton från 517:e amerikanska fallskarmsregementet ner over sodra Frankrike. Deras uppdrag ar att bistå och skydda de allierade styrkorna i deras marsch mot Berlin, men nar de landar mitt i ett fientligt territorium blir de genast attackerade. Tre av fallskarmsjagarna isoleras från gruppen och i ett forsok att slutfora uppdraget och mote upp sin enhet stoter de på en desperat grupp ur den franska motståndsrorelsen. De bestammer sig for att hjalpa till att befria några av de tillfångatagna rebellerna – ett forsok dar de satter sina egna liv på spel. Genom att gora så handlar de i linje med regementets hederskodex – Airborne Creed.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Texas Red
programme.desc: Den sanna historien om legendariske Texas Red, en afroamerikansk man som vildsint jagades utmed prariens sargade landskap av hundratals laglosa cowboys genom Mississippis vintervildmark. Allt for att lagga beslag på den hogst eftertraktade beloningen.

programme.title: The Fourth Musketeer
programme.desc: På uppdrag av sin far reser den unge dArtagnan från landsbygden i Gascogne till Paris, dar han blir indragen i en listig och mycket komplicerad komplott mellan kungens musketorer och kardinal Richelieus gardister. Blod ska spillas, och den som inte ar på sin vakt kommer få satta livet till.

programme.title: Raining in the Mountain
programme.desc: I ett buddhisttempel i Mingdynastins Kina ar det dags for abboten att utse sin eftertradare. Men bland kandidaterna finns det de som framst ar ute efter att stjala den ovarderliga skriften i templets skattkammare. Intriger och allianser uppstår nar personliga ambitioner och andliga stravanden kolliderar.

programme.title: Shockwave
programme.desc: Nar en massiv vulkanisk storm drabbar varlden forsoker geofysikern Kate Ferris overtyga forsvarsdepartementet att det inte ar ett naturligt fenomen. Det ar resultatet av ett seismiskt supervapen, kant som Hell Storm, som aktiverats. Kate måste komma på ett satt att stoppa chockvågen innan den hotar manskligheten.

programme.title: TMNT
programme.desc: Splittra; råttan sensei; kanner att hans fyra tonåriga skoldpaddslarjungar har vuxit isar och behover knyta an for att besegra ett uråldrigt monster.

programme.title: Salt And Fire
programme.desc: En forskare blir kidnappad och slangd ut i en dodsbringande oken dar hon måste kampa mot elementen for att overleva.

programme.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 3
programme.desc: Det hela borjar med att en magisk spira transporterar deras goda van April genom tid och rum, anda till samurajernas Japan. Leonardo och ganget ger sig genast av efter henne, och måste nu besegra den elake Lord Naringa for att radda den insparrade April och återta spiran som lorden kommit over. Annars lar de bli fast i medeltida Japan i eviga tider. Och dar finns ju inte ens några pizzerior…

programme.title: Impact Earth
programme.desc: En astronomiprofessor som jobbat for NASA inser att en destruktiv asteroid ar på kollisionskurs med jorden och måste få sin familj i sakerhet samtidigt som han varnar varlden for denna hotande forodelse.

programme.title: Man On A Ledge (2012)
programme.desc: Vågar du ta nasta steg? Den forrymde fången Nick Cassidy står plotsligt hogt upp på en avsats på en skyskrapa i New York. Kommer han att hoppa? På nolltid har Nick fångat hela stadens och alla mediers uppmarksamhet. Och medan alla tittar upp, ser ingen den utstuderade kupp som ager rum på andra sidan gatan. Hanger dessa båda handelser ihop? Kommer polispsykologen Lydia sanningen på spåren? Och har Nick i sjalva verket en helt annan agenda?

programme.title: Saknad i strid 2 (Missing in Action 2: The Beginning)
programme.desc: Actionstjarnan Chuck Norris återvander som overste James Braddock i denna intensiva, actionfyllda prequel till den ursprungliga succefilmen. Nar kriget rasar i Vietnam blir Braddock och hans man tillfångatagna under en raddningsoperation i luften och fangslade av den hansynslose overste Yin (Soon-Tek Oh), som inte kommer att stoppa for något for att bryta deras anda! For Braddock ar valet klart: han måste befria sina medfångar och forstora lagret! Med navar, kraftiga sprangamnen och ren mod blir han en arme for sig sjalv!

programme.title: Hamburger Hill
programme.desc: Bravo Companys-man står infor en kamp som ar uppforsbacke... uppfor Hamburger Hill. Fjorton krigstrotta soldater kampar for en lera tackt jordhog som ar så namngiven, eftersom den tuggar upp soldater som hackat kott. De kampar for sitt land, sina medsoldater och sina liv. Krig ar helvete, men det har ar varre. Hamburger Hill berattar hur det var, som det verkligen var. Den ar en rå, modig och helt oforsonlig dramatisk skildring av en av de hårdaste striderna i Amerikas blodigaste krig. Detta hande. Hamburger Hill - krig nar den ar som varst, man då de ar som bast.

programme.title: The Condemned 2
programme.desc: Nar han misslyckas med att fånga ledaren for en dodlig spelring blir prisjagaren Will Tanner den jagade — ett manskligt mål i ett spel dar de som ar med måste doda eller bli dodade.

programme.title: Supersnutarna
programme.desc: De alskar fighter och planerar ett stort rån - och de ar filmnes hjaltar!Det har bara gått fem minuter av denna actionkomedi då Terence Hill och Bud Spencer redan forstort tre amerikanska vrålåk och spoat upp deras agare. Matt Kirby (Hill) och Wilbur Walsh (Spencer) ar två hårdslående bråkmakare, men med hjartat på ratta stallet. Efter ett misslyckat rånforsok i Miami hamnar de av misstag på stadens polisskola. Trots att de har svårt att skilja på ratt och fel klarar de utbildningen och utses till motorcykelpoliser. De gor sitt basta for att bli utsparkade ur poliskåren, men hur hårt de an anstranger sig går de ur varje fight som hjaltar!

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Final Shot
programme.desc: Lonnmordaren Frank har lagt sitt tidigare arbete på hyllan och forsoker leva ett till synes vanligt liv tillsammans med flickvannen och hans dotter. En dag kommer en okand maffia boss forbi for att få Franks hjalp att ha ihjal den som tagit livet av hans unga dotter. For att inte dra in sin egen familj i eventuella komplikationer måste Frank fatta ett beslut om att gora stoten åt bossen eller få ro med sin egen sjal?

programme.title: Triassic Hunt
programme.desc: Nar två genetiskt framtagna dinousarer rymmer från laboratoriet kallas en styrka legosoldater in for att fånga dem. Men nar soldaterna inser att dinousarerna ar lika smarta som manniskor borjar en katt och råttalek utan dess like.

programme.title: American Exit
programme.desc: Charlie Bond står infor ett vagskal i livet. Han har nyligen separerat från sin fru och blir ombedd att ta hand om deras son Leo over helgen. Illa tajmat då han just ar i fard med att iscensatta en konstkupp for lite snabba pengar. Leo ar helt ovetandes om planen och bara ser fram emot att får spendera tid med sin efterlangtade pappa. Tatt inpå kommer verkligheten snabbt ikapp Charlie som nu ar i allra hogsta grad en jagad man av skoningslosa torpeder. Hans enda hopp ar att lyckats fly ut ur landet och att få återstalla sin relation till Leo som han vanskott i alla år.

programme.title: Flight World War II
programme.desc: Fångad I en strid mellan Tyska och Allierade styrkor kampar passagerarna i en modern 757 jet for att overleva efter att deras gjort en tidsresa tillbaka till 1940. I deras stravan att overleva lyckas de påverka historien och utgången av Andra Varldskriget.

programme.title: Sightings
programme.desc: Ett science fiction-mysterium om en dysfunktionell familj som bor på en ranch i Texas och hotas av en varelse i skogen. For att kunna overleva hotet måste de samtidigt losa sina egna inre konflikter.

programme.title: Legal Action
programme.desc: Stjarnadvokaten Casey McKay lockas till en liten stad av sin exfru for att forsvara hennes bror som står åtalad for att ha mordat en distriktsåklagare. Casey blottlagger en konspirationsharva som staller honom oga mot oga med mr Gates, stadens allra mest korrupte markexploator. En f.d. marinsoldat hjalper Casey i konflikten nar det står klart att han behover mer an sitt juridiska kunnande for att hålla sig vid liv och radda sin klient.

programme.title: Wild Target
programme.desc: En klumpig yrkesmordare blir foralskad i sitt offer och måste skydda henne från både sin egen organisation och polisen.

programme.title: Spaghettiman
programme.desc: Clark saknar empati for allt och alla. Han skiter fullstandigt i varlden vi lever i och bryr sig knappt om sig sjalv heller. Men efter en incident med en gammal gryta fylld av spaghetti och en trasig mikro går nått fullstandigt snett. Clark forvandlas till en superhjalte som kan bekampa kriminalitet med hjalp av spaghetti. Men det finns en hake, du måste betala honom.

programme.title: Cold Zone
programme.desc: En storm ar på vag. Ingen kan forutsaga den. Ingen kan mata dess storlek. Nu måste en familj overleva den. Och ingen kan soka skydd från stormen, ingen kommer in från kylan…

programme.title: Skurkar och banditer
programme.desc: Tony Roma (Tomas Milian) ar alla tiders halaste gigolo, en sol-och-vårare och skojare specialiserad på att knycka formogna hemmafruars diamanter. Till slut kopplas den hemliga polisen Parker (Bud Spencer) in for att ta fast den lille skojaren. Parker vill helst åka på semester med sin stora familj. Istallet tvingas han nu skydda Tony sedan denne blivit vittne till ett maffiamord. Sjalvklart haglar råsoparna och smockorna nar Parker tar sig an maffiaganget och kastar skurkarna rakt igenom dorrar och vaggar.

programme.title: USS Indianapolis: Men of Courage
programme.desc: I slutet av andra varldskriget fraktade den amerikanska tunga kryssaren USS Indianapolis i hemlighet en av de två atombomber som skulle komma att avsluta kriget. En japansk ubåt anfoll och sankte fartyget. USS Indianapolis uppdrag var så hemligt att fartyget inte anmaldes saknat och ingen visste att fartyget hade sankts forran forst fyra dagar senare. Av de 1197 ombord foljde nastan 300 med sitt fartyg i djupet. De overlevande blev liggande i de hajrika vattnen i Filippinska sjon och tvingades att utstå hunger, torst, hetta, hallucinationer, ideliga hajangrepp och många av sina skeppskamraters dod. Fem dagar senare levde bara 317 man och dessa kunde till slut raddas.

programme.title: Saints and Soldiers: Airborne Creed
programme.desc: Den 15 augusti 1944 hoppar en pluton från 517:e amerikanska fallskarmsregementet ner over sodra Frankrike. Deras uppdrag ar att bistå och skydda de allierade styrkorna i deras marsch mot Berlin, men nar de landar mitt i ett fientligt territorium blir de genast attackerade. Tre av fallskarmsjagarna isoleras från gruppen och i ett forsok att slutfora uppdraget och mote upp sin enhet stoter de på en desperat grupp ur den franska motståndsrorelsen. De bestammer sig for att hjalpa till att befria några av de tillfångatagna rebellerna – ett forsok dar de satter sina egna liv på spel. Genom att gora så handlar de i linje med regementets hederskodex – Airborne Creed.

programme.title: Street Fighter: The Legend Of Chun-Li
programme.desc: Efter det att hennes pappa blivit kidnappad tar Chun-Li steget ner i Hong Kongs brutala undre varld - torstande efter hamnd och på vag mot den ultimata konfrontationen med den storsta fiende hon någonsin kommer att mota. De stålhårda smockorna hanger i luften nar Street Fighter ar tillbaka!

programme.title: Salt And Fire
programme.desc: En forskare blir kidnappad och slangd ut i en dodsbringande oken dar hon måste kampa mot elementen for att overleva.

programme.title: The Provence coast - Marseille and the Côte Bleue
programme.desc: The Provence is famed for its endless fields of laven-der, but this lush landscape also has a beautifully mari-time touch: The Côte Bleue! Small, hidden beaches, charming harbour towns, imposing, craggy bays and a uniquely clear light that has attracted painters includ-ing Cezanne and Braque. The coast derives its name from the deep blue water and extends from Marseille to Martigues. This small town is also known as "The Ven-ice of the North", as it is shaped entirely by water: an inland lake, the sea itself, as well as a connecting canal. In the bays of the Calanques, the steeply-walled coastal inlets in the Mediterranean limestone, Lionel Franc is a cliff diver. His personal record is a...

programme.title: Leap Of The Lynx
programme.desc: On the Iberian Peninsula, primeval landscapes are practically non-existent, so the Iberian lynx has lived on cultivated land for centuries – cattle, horse and pig pastures, cork oak forests, timberland, and even holy sites of pilgrimage. The diversity and beauty of these locations are truly stunning and their character and history as relevant to this story as that of the big cat itself. Until five years ago, both populations of Iberian lynx were quickly fading away. Their fragmented habitats were shrinking even further, they were starved by lack of prey and reduced by epidemics. But now, local authorities, scientists, landowners, and other groups have finally begun to act in unison.

programme.title: Masai Mara: The Big Hunt
programme.desc: When food supply in the Serengeti dwindles, the Masai Mara is a paradise for predators. As the black wildebeests, gazelles, zebras and antelopes make their yearly trip from the south of the Serengeti to the north, nature’s best laid trap, the Mara River in Kenya is waiting ahead. Captivating shots filmed under water show how crocodiles prepare for the Big Hunt while other predators lurk on the banks awaiting their bounty. The biggest problems for the migratory animals are the Mara and the Tarek River, where they have to put their lives at risk to get to the other side. A great number of them die as they jump into the river and break their legs, while others are carried away by the drift...

programme.title: Namibia`s Desert Kingdom
programme.desc: Although the dunes are barren, the dry riverbeds show signs of growth. And out of the heat, vast shapes appear. A herd of desert elephants ambles along the dry riverbed sniffing the ground with their lazy trunks. These remarkable creatures can smell the water underground and know where to find it. An abandoned well attracts a troop of chacma baboons, followed by a small herd of oryx and springbok, and finally a group of jackals. None of them has seen the pride of desert lions lying in wait.

programme.title: Close up with Hippos
programme.desc: This nature documentary shows the many different sides of the Hippo’s lives on one September day in two iconic African locations: the Masai Mara-Nationalpark in Kenya, also the setting for the largest annual animal migration on the planet – one and a half million wildebeests and zebras migrate from the Serengeti to Kenya during this time.

programme.title: Strandwolf
programme.desc: She moves through the seal colony on Namibia’s wild Skeleton Coast with purpose and focus, gingerly stepping around the adults who snap at her heels. She’s searching for smaller prey. Following her is a young German field scientist, Ingrid Wiesel, who has now spent 17 years with Tosca’s clan; tracking, observing, and learning everything she can about one of the world’s least understood and most unusual predators.

programme.title: The Dying King
programme.desc: In the open wilderness of Africa, there are only 20.000 lions living a free life. In the last decade, humans have killed hundreds of thousands– mostly for purely hunting purposes. In the last couple of years, a new industry has developed called the canned hunting, where animals are bred for 4-5 years then released into a confined area. This confined area is created for the sole purpose optimizing the odds of the hunter obtaining a kill. The corpse of the dead, often male, lion is thereby treated as a trophy. Tourists pay up to 40, 000 USD for this privilege.

programme.title: The Incredible Five - A Cheetahs Tale
programme.desc: Cheetahs are the high-speed hunters of the Savannah. Few attempt to take on larger prey than gazelles or smallish antelopes. But on occasion, the predatory cats reveal their surprisingly different side. In the Northern Serengeti, a group of male cheetahs emerges and turns all we know about them upside down. Males are usually loners or live in small groups, but here we have five tomcats hunting together as one. It is actually, the largest alliance of the animals ever seen! This film has many stories to tell about the sleek hunters.

programme.title: The Original Fight Club: Animal Fights Caught on Camera
programme.desc: There are many reasons for animals to fight and each have their own weapons and rules of combat. They rarely fight without good reason: usually to defend a patch, secure a meal or to attract a mate. With so many reasons for warfare, life can be a never ending battle – for all creatures no matter how great or small, life is a struggle – but they endure – perhaps because there is a fighter in us all …

programme.title: The Cape of Wild Animals, Episode 5
programme.desc: The movie focuses on committed animal rights activists, who fight for the lives of their charges every day, in diverse protection projects and rescue centres along the South African Garden Route.

programme.title: Lions On The Move
programme.desc: Kevin Richardson shares an extraordinary bond with Africa’s most fearsome predators. Together with them, he has experienced some real adventures. However, transporting 27 lions and 14 hyenas to a new home presents a different challenge.The lions new home will be a sanctuary on the edge of Dinokeng, a South African game reserve spanning 18,000 square metres. The huge task ahead includes planning and designing the new enclosures, and securing permits to move the animals.

programme.title: Lions On The Move
programme.desc: Not only are the animals regularly rotated into new enclosures to prevent repetitive behaviour developing out of boredom, but Kevin also has to practice loading them in and out of the van. Can the reluctant lions and hyenas eventually be persuaded to get on board with the move?

programme.title: White Lions: Born Wild
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 White Lions: Born Wild - Episode 1: Against all Odds
programme.desc: The two sisters are born as white as snow in May 2009 in South Africa’s Kruger Park. Growing up in this vast, wild wilderness they must not only overcome the same survival challenges that all young lion cubs face, they must also overcome the threats their high visibility brings. In the African bush, anything unusual stands out and is often eliminated by eagle-eyed predators. Will our cubs survive? The odds are stacked against them – 80 percent of all newborn lion cubs don’t make it to adulthood.

programme.title: White Lions: Born Wild
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 White Lions: Born Wild - Episode 2: Fight for Survival
programme.desc: ‘White Lions – Born Wild’ is a true wildlife story, with strong characters and closely studied behaviour. We follow the cubs’ progress as they embark on the pathway to adulthood, learning to hunt, learning to avoid danger, learning to live in their white coats. This is a strong behaviour-led film, a coming-of-age story of a very rare and unusual pair of lions. Through their eyes, we learn what it is really like to be a lion in Africa.

programme.title: Dust And Stripes
programme.desc: In a never-ending quest for grass and water, the striped herds undertake an annual epic trek across the vast lunar landscape of the Kalahari’s Makgadikgadi Pans. Most of the year, the Makgadikgadi is an inhospitable wasteland of windswept, salt-encrusted pans. For the area’s water-dependent zebra, the Boteti River on the western edge of the pans is a dry-season lifeline. However, it is also a death trap, with lions waiting in ambush and crocodiles lurking in dark riverside caves.

programme.title: Wild Switzerland
programme.desc: Gentle, green meadows, rugged rock faces, mysterious lakes, dense forests, tall mountains, low-lying river deltas, quietly meandering mountain streams and smack dab in the middle, a unique fauna - THIS is Switzerland! We trace the elementary power of nature and present animals and plants in landscapes that have hardly ever been touched by mankind. Switzerland is an alpine country, but it is also Europes surge tank. Rivers such as the Rhine and the Rhone have their sources here. Glaciers, crevasses, icy cold caves and the underwater dome of the Verzasca are the unusual settings we chose for this film. We meet with rare, selected animal species and present their behavioural patterns, such...

programme.title: Wild Skagerrak
programme.desc: The strait that connects the North Sea with the Baltic, with depths of over 700 metres, is notorious for its dangerously strong currents. But currents also mean food and therefore nourishment for the large swarms of fish that inhabit the region. The sea grass meadows are comparable with those off the Californian coast. Harbour seals, grey seals and orcas hunt here, as do the rare black mouth cat shark and porpoises. Close by, catfish mate, which in itself is quite spectacular and never caught on film in this way before. Lions mane jellyfish with nettle threads of up to 30 metres in length make their way through the open sea. Skagerraks coastal regions are amongst the most beautiful and...

programme.title: Wild Sardinia
programme.desc: Sardinia has always been the epitome of pure wilderness, an emerald of volcanic origin in the Mediterranean. 1900 metres of coastline and an infinite maze of offshore islands. But Sardinia also has other facets: green valleys, rugged mountains, murmuring brooks, mysterious ruins and a unique fauna. Just off of Sardinias coast is an untouched underwater paradise - uniquely beautiful, but also dangerous. Pilot whales, dolphins and mobula rays populate the waters at Capo Testa in the north of the island. In the west, the lagoons of Cabras represent a wild landscape of lakes in which thousands of flamingos live and hunt the red brine shrimps. In addition to the flamingos, grey and purple...

programme.title: Secrets of the Mediterranean
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Secrets of the Mediterranean, Ep.1
programme.desc: The contours of the Mediterranean have changed during the course of its history. Near Gibraltar, Africa was once connected to the European continent. When the land bridge at Gibraltar collapsed, the Mediterranean basin filled up again. The Suez Canal is today connected to the Red Sea. This route enables animals to reach the Mediterranean, where they cause problems.

programme.title: Secrets of the Mediterranean
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Secrets of the Mediterranean, Ep. 2
programme.desc: Rugged rocks, blue sea and idyllic, sandy beaches - this is the Mediterranean as we know it. But this impression is deceptive: the Mediterranean is under constant change. The continents are moving towards one another. Animals, that have to survive under such extreme conditions, must find a way to escape the dangers. Between deserts and volcanoes, the challenges for the animals are enormous.

programme.title: Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape: Episode 1
programme.desc: A few thousand years ago, there were bare moraine ridges and barren meltwater valleys here. A landscape born in the last ice age, characterized by the edge of the Alps, gentle hills, moors, and lakes. And by cultural richness, not only on the islands in Lake Chiemsee, with their famous monasteries and castles. Long before King Ludwig II, the first people settled in the Chiemgau region. Finds of hunting weapons from the Neanderthal era prove that the land was inhabited even during the ice age, probably because there was plenty of game to hunt. During the Bronze Age, one of the most important trade routes from the mountains to the Alpine foothills passed through here. Then came the Celts...

programme.title: Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape: Episode 2
programme.desc: Three times in the past two decades, the Chiemsee area has experienced "once-in-a-century" floods. Climate, wildlife, and landscape have changed, and it seems this transformation is accelerating. Species living in the flood zones are developing sophisticated survival strategies. Knot ants, for instance, place their queen in the middle and form a raft with their bodies, even conquering new habitats. Flooding is less of a disaster for nature and impacts humans more significantly.

programme.title: Europes Wild River - The Elbe - 1.000 Miles of Wildlife and Nature
programme.desc: The river rises in the Czech Giant Mountains. Here it is called the Labe. After Děčín it flows into Germany and is called Elbe. There are various explanations for the origin of the river name "Elbe". One often mentioned is the Latin name of the river "albia", which means "bright water". This would also explain why the stream is referred to with the feminine article "the Elbe", since the Latin term "albia" is also feminine. Rather poetic than linguistically probable, however, is the explanation that elves (Middle High German: alb) scurrying around the pines in the white river mists could have helped the river to get its name. Geographically, the river can be divided into different...

programme.title: Alpine Lakes - Dark Depths and Icy Heights
programme.desc: This is a nature documentary, which leads us into the fascinating world of deep mountain lakes. We conquer ice palaces of unsuspected beauty. In the freezers, in which elves, fairies and mountain trolls once did their mischief, we move, using a special breathing technique and with special cameras in search of nocturnal hunters, whose eyes are equipped with residual light amplifying receptors.

programme.title: The Secret world of Herbs
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 The Secret World of Herbs - In Provence
programme.desc: Its native fragrant flowers and aromatic herbs have made the Provence a brand known worldwide. The wealth of flora found in this region, between the French Alps and the Mediterranean, is unequalled among the French provinces. Around Sault, near Mont Ventoux, the valleys and high plains are carpeted with bright violet: In the hot climate of the South of France, lavender blooms and exudes its fragrance. Monastic healers have been using its aromatic medicinal oil since the Middle Ages. And today an entire industry is based on the trade with this fragrant flower. Yet the livelihood of Provençal lavender farmers is imperiled. In France’s major lavender-growing region, the “Plateau de...

programme.title: The Secret world of Herbs
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 The Secret World of Herbs - In India
programme.desc: In India, herbs play an everyday role hardly equalled anywhere in the world. From the tropical green south to the mountains of the northern Himalayas, herbs lend fragrance to joss sticks and soaps, and flavor to the cuisine. And, above all, herbs heal. Six thousand varieties of plants are used in India, and most are harvested in the wild – where they are becoming depleted. The ever rising need for herbal medicine for the subcontinent’s 1.3 billion inhabitants comes on top of the demand of its growing middle class for herbal-based cosmetics. As a result, certain herbs have become scarce, while others have already vanished entirely. Most of the herbs in India are harvested in the wild. The...

programme.title: The Secret world of Herbs
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 The Secret World of Herbs - In Latin America
programme.desc: Healing effects, fragrance, and intense flavor – the benefits of herbs were discovered by the indigenous peoples of South America long before Spanish conquistadores subdued the continent. Even today, in the remote regions of South America, life without herbs is unthinkable. For many inhabitants, they provide the sole medicine. For more than two thousand years, this wisdom of the healing powers of nature has been passed down from generation to generation. In Bolivia, the film accompanies ethnobiologist Rainer Bussmann on one of his expeditions documenting which herbs the locals use against which illnesses. The German scientist has spent the last 15 years in the region, focussed on...

programme.title: The Secret world of Herbs
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 The Secret World of Herbs - In the Alps
programme.desc: Secluded for many centuries in inaccessible valleys, the inhabitants of the Alps had no alternative but to rely on the healing powers of nature. A knowledge of herbs was deeply rooted in these mountain-dwellers’ everyday lives – until the twentieth century, when this wisdom became eclipsed by modern academic medicine. Today, Alpine herbs are witnessing a revival, as public interest in regional natural treasures grows. The potential of Alpine herbs is far from exhausted. In the Berchtesgaden Alps, the film shows Hubsi Ilsanker at work as a root-digger, a back-breaking job that has scarcely changed in four hundred years. Authorized by a special historic permit to supply the oldest gentian...

programme.title: The Secret world of Herbs
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 The Secret world of Herbs - In the Balkans
programme.desc: In the pristine nature and mild climate of southeastern Europe grows a unique diversity of wild plants. Far removed from major industry and polluted soils, the Balkan countries have become the largest exporter of herbs in Europe. In Bulgaria alone, more than 300,000 people work with domestic plants. The business is becoming increasingly lucrative. The film takes us to the Croatian coast. On the Adriatic island of Cres, the audience meets Mladen Dragoslavić. In May, when the sage begins to blossom, this beekeeper has one month to produce his income for an entire year – always with the goal of creating the best sage honey in the Balkans. Given a choice, the bees would never choose sage, for...

programme.title: Italy My Love
programme.desc: In ten coastal areas of Italy, we encounter people that have a very special relationship with their region. All of them love their country, their traditions and their work. We met with enthusiasts and hedonists that permitted us to take a glimpse into their everyday lives. Young Italians, who have rediscovered nature and its treasures. Others, that preserve the beauty, archaeologists that apply whole new methods, farmers that only cultivate that which the soil needs. Fishermen, who fish in the same way as it was done a century ago and tough, young men who play and dance the Tarantella. Dolphins, giant sea turtles and pink flamingos, which are researched, nursed back to health or simply...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Night of Horror at Devils Plateau (Marie-Jeanne Meyer Case) - On June 18, 2011, Marie-Jeanne Meyer, 17-years old, waved goodbye to her little sister before leaving for her daily jog on the heights of Tournon in Ardèche. She never came back. Three days later, her mutilated body was found in a freshly dug pit, near an area known to be cursed, "The Devils Plateau." Whats more, the crime scene looked like a mystical ritual ... Was it a ritual murder? Revenge? An unfortunate encounter? ...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Mysterious Murder at the Farm (Valerie Bary Case)- On Friday, March 26, 2004, in the region of Dijon, Laurent Bary came home from his work to discover the lifeless body of his wife, Valerie, bathing in a pool of blood. According to the investigators initial findings, the 38-year-old nurses aid had been stabbed several times, seeming to validate the theory of a robbery gone wrong.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On July 13, 2011, two boaters retrieved a suitcase that was floating in the bay of Lorient. Inside, they discovered the tied up corpse of a man.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Bloody Christmas next to the Leman lake (CASE OF RUTH LÉGERET) - On January 4, 2006, Ruth Legeret was found dead in the middle of a pool of blood at her luxurious property in Vevey, Switzerland. Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: September 16 2005. The lifeless body of Audrey Jouannet, 24, is found hidden under the bed in her small apartment in Soisy-sur-Seine. It soon becomes apparent that the young woman has been tortured at length before being strangled. But surprisingly, though the highly meticulous murderer has taken care to leave no sign of his passage, the autopsy reveals traces of sperm on the victim. It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Sylvain Dromard finds the body of his wife Laurence lying in a pool of blood in the kitchen. The crime was particularly violent and the theory of a burglary that went wrong is soon excluded. But investigators dont understand who could want the adorable hairdresser of Saint-Martin-dAblois dead. During the investigation, the work of profilers will enable them to draw a very precise portrait of the murderer...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: After an ordinary dinner, Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell suffer severe abdominal pains.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Nelly Cremel, 39, leaves her home to go jogging... never to return. Eight days later, after a vast search campaign, her body is found. Theres no doubt that its murder. The case soon ignites public opinion, even inflaming passions at the highest level of the state. The clues lead investigators on a number of trails, from the shadows of the French secret service to a manhunt for a possible sex maniac, in a case of murder most foul.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Willy Pomonti, a retired architect, is found savagely murdered in his opulent villa in La Celle-Saint-Cloud, near Paris. It soon becomes clear that the man has been tortured prior to death. At several points during this extraordinary enquiry, police will feel theyre holding the culprit... It will take them ten years to finally shed light on this particularly violent crime.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The lifeless body of Christophe Lejard is found by his son just metres from their home. The man was shot in the head as he was getting into his car to go to work. A veritable execution, which at first glance doesnt square with the profile of the quiet family man. Yet behind the appearances, the investigation gradually reveals all the hate and resentment that revolved around the victim.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A man walks into a gendarmerie near Saint-Malo to report that his wife has been missing since the previous day. The couple are going through a divorce, but this mother would never have left her seven children alone! An extensive search is undertaken but the woman cannot be found. What has happened to Adeline Piet? The investigation spans several years and experiences many twists.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The corpse of Priscillia Ciatti, 14, is discovered by the side of a field, a few hundred metres from her family home. The teenager has been stabbed sixty times with a knife and -an extra sordid detail - a devil mask is found next to her body. Was Priscillia the victim of a prowler? A serial killer? A maniac inspired by a horror movie? Investigators soon find that the young girl felt she was being watched, and even threatened...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: In the early hours of the morning, Mathilde Croguennec, 18, attending "Teknival" in Brittany, is found at the foot of a tree with her throat cut. Investigators face the task of finding the killer from among the 43,000 participants of this huge open-air festival of electronic music, where drink and drugs are consumed in abundance. An unusual investigation that leads the police down a number of false avenues.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Arriving at her work, the secretary of a small firm in the suburbs of Geneva finds the body of Jean-Raymond Blatti, the companys new accountant. The man is lying in a pool of blood and, on his belly, the murderer has written "DIRTY RAPIST". Yet Jean-Raymond Blatti was never charged with sexual assault. Over the course of the investigation, this inscription will appear as one of the many mysteries of this case which is particularly rich in twists and turns.

programme.desc: Having killed his wife and buried her in the basement, Dr. Crippen believed he had escaped on a ship to Canada. But the police managed to hunt him down.

programme.title: The Brides In The Bath Killer
programme.desc: George Smith had many aliases. He needed them for his many wives who he would soon murder in order to claim the inheritance.

programme.desc: Edith Thompson and Frederick Bywaters were in love. But the young couple was convicted for murdering her husband in a case that shocked society and fascinated Hitchcock.

programme.title: The Blackout Ripper
programme.desc: It was WWII and London was rocked by the Blitz from the planes flying above. But down on the streets below another terrible danger lurked in the shadows.

programme.title: Herculaneum Scrolls: Unraveling History
programme.desc: The eruption of Mount Vesuvius is renowned for its decimation of Pompeii, but nearby, an equally impressive Roman settlement known as Herculaneum was lost to history.

programme.title: Part 1: Rise of Civilization
programme.desc: In the region that includes the Mediterranean, the Aegean, Mesopotamia and Egypt, the Bronze Age arrived about 3000 BC and lasted nearly 2000 years. What singled out this period and the new societies and cities that emerged? The development of formal writing is one among several important factors.

programme.title: Part 2: Masters Of Trade
programme.desc: Trade, and in particular trade in luxury goods, drove the commerce economies of the Bronze Age. This is the time when the first super powers in history, Egypt and Mesopotamia, emerge and dominate the "world" stage of the Mediterranean and Aegean seas and surrounding areas.

programme.title: Part 3: Conquest And Collapse
programme.desc: The Bronze Age had the first large urban centers, powerful kingdoms and armies, writing, and trade routes across vast areas. What led to the collapse of the city-state entities and the end of the Bronze Age? Possibly a perfect storm of uncontrollable factors that are still being researched.

programme.title: Episode 1: The Rise Of Civilization
programme.desc: About 8,000 BC, in a few select places some people begin to experiment with a new way of harvesting energy. They’re growing their own crops.

programme.title: Episode 2: The Age Of Discovery
programme.desc: Columbus has no idea that because of Earth’s geology and geography he wont get to his destination…or how that failure made his voyage one of the most influential.

programme.title: Episode 3: The Industrial Revolution And Modern Warfare
programme.desc: How do prehistoric forests link to the development of steam engines, and the rise of modern industry?

programme.desc: In this episode, we learn how early Viking society developed, what the sacred rituals really were, and what role women played in Viking religion.

programme.desc: Ships carried Nordic warriors all the way from their Scandinavian homes to lands of conquest. How were these ergonomic ships built and what made them so special?

programme.desc: The Vikings were fighting machines, plundering lands from central Asia to North America and defeated the armies of the greatest empires. What was their secret?

programme.desc: Watch as the Mars Perseverance Rover makes its historic landing on the Red Planet. We take you inside the harrowing February 18, 2021 landing and its science mission.

programme.title: Capturing A Black Hole In Our Milky Way
programme.desc: Astronomers linked radio dishes around the world to create the “Event Horizon Telescope” and have utilized this tool to photograph a supermassive black hole.

programme.title: Private Moonshot
programme.desc: A non-profit organization established in 2011 is aiming to land the first Israeli spacecraft on the Moon. This is the story of their attempt and the excitement of being the first private company to have a spacecraft launched with the intention of going to and landing on the moon.

programme.title: Modern Day Killer Asteroid
programme.desc: 66 million years ago, an asteroid slammed into Mexico’s Yucatán Peninsula, causing a dinosaur mass extinction. Whats in store for humanity if it happens again?

programme.desc: Hayabusa2 just became the first spacecraft to take subsurface samples of an asteroid. How did they do it?

programme.desc: The latest developments in space technology continue to reveal the wonders of our solar system. With new moons recently spotted orbiting Saturn, the gas giant has taken the lead in our cosmic neighborhoods moon count.

programme.desc: This is an inside look at NASAs groundbreaking Artemis Program, the spacecraft, and the people who will bring humanity one step closer to the moon, Mars, and beyond.

programme.title: First Images: The James Webb Telescope
programme.desc: The dawn of a new era in astronomy has begun as the world gets its first look at the full capabilities of NASA’s James Webb Space Telescope.

programme.title: Touching the Sun
programme.desc: NASAs Parker Probe Plus is on a mission to learn more about the Sun -- flying through dangerous radiation to become the closest spaceship to orbit our Sun.

programme.title: Crisis On Apollo 13

programme.desc: Jaques (Brian Cox – THE BOURNE IDENTITY) ager en sjaskig bar, som fungerar som ett andra hem for en brokig skara professionella drinkare. Jaques sjalv ar fast besluten att supa och roka sig till dods. Nar han moter den unge hemlose Lucas (Paul Dano – THERE WILL BE BLOOD), som också gett upp hoppet om livet, tycker han sig ha hittat den perfekte arvingen till baren. Jaques borjar lara Lucas sitt kungadomes manschauvernistiska lagar: inga nya kunder, ingen personlig kontakt med gasterna, och absolut inga kvinnor! Lucas lar sig fort, men vanskapen satts på prov då den olyckliga och vackra April (Isild Le Besco) soker skydd i baren.

programme.title: Evil Stepmom
programme.desc: Ett tvillingpar vill hjalpa sin pappa att borja dejta igen och skapar en profil på en dejtingsajt åt honom. Det drojer inte lange forran han får svar. En av tvillingflickorna blir van med pappans dejts dotter. Snart inser hon att det ar något som inte stammer. Men hur ska hon få sin nyforalskade pappa att inse allvaret?

programme.title: Mazes and Monsters
programme.desc: Robbie och hans collegekompisar ar alla besatta av rollspelet "Mazes and Monsters". Men spelen tar en marklig vandning nar Robbie borjar få visioner efter att de spelat en session på ett mystiskt, lokalt landmarke.

programme.title: Fast Girls
programme.desc: Nar kaxiga och gatsmarta Shania (Lenora Crichlow) traffar den ambitiosa medelklasstjejen Lisa (Lily James) kolliderar deras två varldar på loparbanan med explosiva foljder. De två sprintertjejerna kampar for att kvala in till VM i friidrott och moter tuffa motgångar och bitter rivalitet på sin dramatiska, hjartevarmande och inspirerande resa.

programme.title: Brain On Fire
programme.desc: Susannah Cahalan har nyligen avslutat sina universitetsstudier och lever dromlivet i New York. Hon ar en lovande journalist på New York Post och foralskad i musikern Stephen. Hennes chef ger henne det stora uppdraget som ska rivstarta hennes karriar och livet kan inte bli battre. Snart borjar saker och ting gå fel. Susannah drabbas av en influensa som inte vill ge sig, hon glommer saker och missar deadlines på jobbet. Hon hor att folk pratar om henne, ar overtygad om att Stephen har en annan flickvan och hon kan inte kontrollera sin kropp. Det blir snart varre; Susannah borjar få våldsamma anfall och hennes alltmer psykotiska upptradande innebar att hon standigt måste overvakas.

programme.title: Bekas
programme.desc: Tidigt 90-tal, Saddam Husseins regim har satt stor press på den kurdiska delen av Irak. Två hemlosa kurdiska pojkar ser Superman på stadens forsta biograf och bestammer sig for att ta sig till Amerika. For att komma dit behover de pass, pengar och en hel del tur. Tyvarr har de inget av detta men de borjar andå resan som ska ta dem mot drommen om Amerika.

programme.title: The Room
programme.desc: Trotta på det hetsiga storstadslivet och alla krav flyttar Kate och Matt in i sitt dromhus på landet. Men det gamla huset hyser sannerligen hemligheter och snart upptacker de ett val undangomt rum. Ett rum som har den fantastiska egenskapen att frammana och materialisera exakt vad de onskar sig. Dock ar ingen lycka komplett utan odesdigra konsekvenser: det som uppstår i rummet kan aldrig lamna det utan att tyna bort. Och det Kate och Matt onskar sig mest… ar ett barn.

programme.title: Incendies
programme.desc: Nar notarien Lebel (Remy Girard) ska lasa upp Nawals testamente for hennes barn Jeanne och Simon, upptacker de två kuvert: ett till den far de trodde var dod, och ett till en bror som de inte visste om. Detta ar borjan på en upptacktsresa i deras doda mors fotspår, och Jeanne och Simon kan borja pussla ihop historien om kvinnan som fott och fostrat dem. Det blir en berattelse om hat, krig och enastående mod. Och till slut återstår bara en pusselbit: att hitta deras okande bror. Den enda ledtråden ar den speciella tatuering av tre svarta prickar som han har på foten. Kanadas Oscarsbidrag 2011.

programme.title: Camp X-Ray
programme.desc: Kristen Stewart spelar huvudrollen i Peter Sattlers hyllade debutfilm Camp X-Ray. Hon spelar Amy Cole, en ung kvinna som tar varvning i amerikanska militaren i tron att hon kommer att skickas till Irak eller Afghanistan. Istallet blir hon stationerad som vakt på ett okant militarfangelse, med tuffa villkor for såval basens fångar som de få kvinnliga militarer som arbetar dar.

programme.title: Tillbaka till Yorkshire
programme.desc: Arthur Morrison får reda på att han har cancer och att han bara har några veckor kvar att leva. Hans vuxna son Blake reser till Yorkshire for att bo hos sin mamma i byn dar han vaxte upp. Nar Arthurs tillstånd forvarras ser Blake tillbaka på sitt forhållande med pappan. Han minns saker de gjort tillsammans, fortroligheten mellan dem och aven de forbistringar de haft. Nar fadern dor borjar Morrison fundera kring det band de haft. Han ger tydligt uttryck for motsattningar, frustration, karlek och forlust som alla ar delar i det komplicerade forhållande som finns mellan en far och hans son.

Hon hor att folk pratar om henne, ar overtygad om att Stephen har en annan flickvan och hon kan inte kontrollera sin kropp. Det blir snart varre; Susannah borjar få våldsamma anfall och hennes alltmer psykotiska upptradande innebar att hon standigt måste overvakas.

programme.title: Dinner Rush
programme.desc: Dinner Rush utspelar sig under vad som från borjan inte tycks vara något annat an en helt vanlig jaktig kvall på Louis Cropas (Danny Aiello) populara restaurang Gigino i det fashionabla TriBeCa-kvarteret i New York. En gång var trattorian en enkel familjerestaurang men nu har den forvandlats till kvarterets mesta innekrog, stallet dar alla vill bli sedda. Detta mycket tack vare krogaren Cropas son Udos (Edoardo Ballerini) innovativa matlagningskonst som kommit att bli stallets kannetecken. Och just den har kvallen ar restaurangen som ett kalejdoskop av livet i dagens New York...

programme.title: Auggie
programme.desc: Felix Greystone har en bit kvar till pensionsåldern, men foretaget pressar honom att gå i fortidspension. I avskedsgåva får han ett par smartglasogon, som vacker anvandarens storsta drommar till liv. Nar Felix frus karriar tar fart och dottern borjar bli sjalvstandig inser Felix hur ensam han kanner sig. For att fly den plågsamma ensamheten fordjupar Felix sig allt mer i sina smartglasogons varld, vilket påfrestar Felix relation till familjen ytterligare.

programme.title: Gringa
programme.desc: En olycklig tonårstjej rymmer till Mexiko for att hitta den pappa hon aldrig kant. Tillsammans lar de sig att en familj kan bli hel igen, aven om de bara har de bitar som saknas.

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: Equals
programme.desc: I en utopisk varld, dar våld och brott i princip ar utplånade via genetisk eliminering av kanslor, lever personer som Nia och Silas ett lugnt, handelselost och dronarlikt liv. De arbetar med att producera informationsmaterial på ett stort kontor och utvaxlar enbart artighetsfraser. Livet ar enkelt, anda till dess att ett rykte borjar florera: en sjukdom som orsakar att manniskor visar kanslor har brutit ut. Om det upptacks av overheten skickas de infekterade ivag, for att aldrig återvanda. Silas misstanker att han bar på sjukdomen och nar det bekraftas, blir han en paria. Trots det dras han till Nia, som också ar infekterad men har lyckats dolja symptomen battre an han sjalv.

programme.title: Evil Stepmom
programme.desc: Ett tvillingpar vill hjalpa sin pappa att borja dejta igen och skapar en profil på en dejtingsajt åt honom. Det drojer inte lange forran han får svar. En av tvillingflickorna blir van med pappans dejts dotter. Snart inser hon att det ar något som inte stammer. Men hur ska hon få sin nyforalskade pappa att inse allvaret?

programme.title: Albert Nobbs
programme.desc: Albert ar en forsynt man som doljer en stor hemlighet, han ar egentligen en kvinna som tvingats kla och bete sig som en man for att komma bort från fattigdom. En dag moter Albert en annan manniska i samma situation och han borjar dromma om ett liv i frihet utan hemligheter. Albert Nobbs ar en stark och rorande film med en stjarnspackad rollista.

programme.title: Journeyman
programme.desc: Efter att ha vunnit en tuff titelmatch på poang, kollapsar mellanviktsmastaren Matty Burton. Resan for att få tillbaka minnet och formågan att tala och rora sig blir hans tuffaste match någonsin och priset kan bli skyhogt då relationen till frun Emma och dottern Mia står på spel.

programme.title: Enter the Void
programme.desc: Regissoren till 2000-talets mest okanda film ar tillbaka med ett verk som inte liknar något annat: en kanslomassigt omtumlande och visuellt overvaldigande mardromsresa genom liv, dod och återfodelse. Prisbelonade Enter the Void ar en mork, men inte desto mindre fargsprakande odysse sedd genom den doende huvudpersonens hallucinerande ogon. I Tokyos neonupplysta natt blir den unge knarklangaren Oscar skjuten. Vore det inte for hans syster hade historien slutat dar.

programme.desc: Systrarna Eve och Lacey onskar sig en jul precis som den i filmens varld. Innan de vet ordet av så upptacker de att dem ar fast i vad som faktiskt ar en julfilm. De vaknar upp i den sagolika staden ”Christmas Town”, den perfekta staden med den perfekta julen, dar allt bara ar perfekt. Ju mer de utforskar allt som har med hogtiden att gora inser de att perfektion kanske inte den ratta meningen for en traditionsenlig jul. Det kanske finns en annan magi med sonderbranda pepparkakor och overkokta julskinkor…?

programme.title: Mr. Christmas
programme.desc: Tom har byggt en karriar att hjalpa klienter finna den perfekta presenten till sin alskade. Julruschen tar fart och hans basta van Paul ber om en tjanst att hitta en present till hans flickvan Jenny. Tom hamnar snabbt i ett dilemma nar han lar kanna Jenny battre och inser att han sjalv håller på att foralska sig i sin vans flickvan. Uppdraget narmar sig sitt slut och Tom våndas over att hans enda chans att hitta sin sjalsvan håller på att rinna ur handerna for honom.

programme.desc: Nar en kand modell återvander till sin småstad fore jul- traffar hon sin barndomsvan som nu har en dotter och en gård. programme.title: A is for Apple
programme.desc: Heres a tongue twister: Theresa, tuna, tangerine! In this episode, host Theresa Visintin picks her favourite letter, "T," and introduces us to scrumptious recipes using tuna and tangerine. Theresa loves tuna and Italian cuisine, so naturally she combines both to create a mouth-watering pasta with some savoury tomato, olive, and tuna sauce. Next, Theresa satisfies her sweet tooth with a decadent tangerine parfait! Using the sweet juice of the tangerine, Theresa creates gelatin, with a hint of orange liqueur. She tops it all off by whipping up a fluffy cream to complete this sweet treat. Then its time for a real challenge: tuna and tangerine in one recipe!

programme.title: A is for Apple
programme.desc: In this "H" challenge, Chef Lauren Gulyas decides to take on the unique flavours of halibut and horseradish. She starts with a perfectly prepared prosciutto wrapped halibut, pairing the buttery flavour of the fish with the saltiness of the cured meat. Throw in some dill potatoes and youve got a beautifully balanced dish. Next up, Chef Lauren show us how to make a delightful roast beef dip with a zesty horseradish sauce using carrots, vinegar, mayo and a little lemon. Finally, she is challenged to make a dish that combines both ingredients, and does she ever deliver!

programme.title: A is for Apple
programme.desc: In this letter "P" challenge, Chef Robert Jewell showcases his vegetarian skills using pecans and peppers. Despite his cowboy roots, Robert shows us he can kick it with vegetarians by cooking up a juicy meatless "meatloaf" using pecans. But, no "meatloaf" would be complete without a gravy! Robert fries up earthy portobello mushrooms before adding a special ingredient to thicken the gravy, you guessed it -- pecans! Now, on to peppers. Robert doubles up, using both the vegetable and seasoning, to make a delicious red pepper coulis with herb and pepper crusted beef tenderloin. Robert goes a little nuts when he prepares his final recipe using both pecans and peppers.

programme.title: Wales

programme.title: Newfoundland and Labrador, Canada

programme.sub-title: S02 : E01 Travel Quest S2 - "Cultural Indonesia"
programme.desc: Of all bucket list items, one stands out above the rest—seeing one of the original reasons for starting the UNESCO World Heritage sites—the massive temple of Borobudur.

programme.title: Mexico: Tequila: Does it need to come from certain regions of Mexico?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E07 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Mexico: Tequila: Does it need to come from certain regions of Mexico?"
programme.desc: In the land of tequila, Liesel gets the skinny on the premium export of Jalisco, blue agave tequila. From harvesting agave with the legendary jimadores, to understanding the process of distillation, Liesel is on the hunt to appreciate and understand the production requirements of this spirit that makes it what it is. Are they worth it only if they’re from Jalisco or can they be made somewhere else for cheaper and better..? Liesel finds out!

programme.title: Los Angeles: Food trucks: are they any good?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Los Angeles: Food trucks: are they any good?"
programme.desc: It’s a well known fact that Los Angeles is the trendsetter for entertainment, fashion, and outlandish celebrity exploits. But is it the same story with the food? Liesel explores the food truck bubble to figure out what started the craze, why its so popular, and more importantly, is the food any good?

programme.title: Gran Canaria
programme.sub-title: S01 : E10 Running the World S1 - "Gran Canaria"
programme.desc: Brothers Max and Benj Cave are challenged to create a run through an abandoned water park on the island of Gran Canaria.

programme.title: Jamaica
programme.sub-title: S01 : E11 Running the World S1 - "Jamaica"
programme.desc: Brothers Max and Benj Cave are challenged to create a unique run in an unusal setting on the Island of Jamaica.

programme.sub-title: S01 : E12 Travels with the Bondi Vet S1 - "South Pacific Paradise"
programme.desc: In this episode of Travels With the Bondi Vet, Chris visits a city with more pets than children, experiences a 3-hour holiday in this south pacific paradise and goes on a 600 kilometer journey in the Australian outback to deliver some mail.

programme.title: Tofu
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Paradise Kitchen Bali S1 - "Tofu"
programme.desc: Discover the delicious and nutritious world of tofu with Lauren as she experiments with various textures and flavors, pushing the soybean to its limits to create amazing dishes like Scramble tofu and the sweet-spicy delight of Tahu Gejrot.

programme.title: Mushroom
programme.sub-title: S01 : E09 Paradise Kitchen Bali S1 - "Mushroom"
programme.desc: Lauren dives into the fascinating world of mushrooms, exploring their flavors, textures, and health benefits. She shows how to make savory mushroom sausage rolls and delicious mushroom steaks, showcasing the versatility of these earthy ingredients.

programme.title: Shaoxing
programme.desc: Join host Tianran He in the historic water town of Shaoxing, famed for its yellow wine. Traversing its canals by boat, Tianran discovers why its said there are 10,000 bridges in Shaoxing.

programme.title: Haikou
programme.desc: Welcome to Haikou, also known as the Coconut City! Join Tianran experiencing the culinary culture and urban character of this tropical paradise. From light and sweet coconut chicken hotpot to refreshing herbal desserts and spicy rice soup.

programme.title: Hainans Four Famous Dishes
programme.sub-title: S02 : E12 Foodwise S2 - "Hainans Four Famous Dishes"
programme.desc: The stunning east coast of Hainan in southeast China, attract numerous visitors to travel. Hainan’s four famous dishes are chicken, duck, goat and crab.

programme.title: Philippines
programme.desc: The nation of 7,000 islands has no problems with beach, sun, or sea; but they suffer tremendously with cuisine image. Jonathan lands in Manila to discover the top chefs are well aware of the issue and, following their advice, he launches off on an expedition to find part of the solution. Driving from headhunting tribal villages, to step-back-in-time colonial towns, to restaurants in the shadow of the American military behemoth an intriguing story slowly pieces together. In the dense jungle one treasure stays buried while another comes literally out of the woodwork. But danger always lurks.. zombie moray eels, landslide prone passes, and forbidden fields behind the rice paddies.

programme.title: Finland
programme.desc: Finland is that one Nordic country that is never on the global cuisine radar. However, the reserved Finns have been quietly perfecting their craft of foraging culture and incorporating it into their unique cuisine. Jonathan Legg explores the entire expanse of the country to understand it’s cuisine, and the ethos of the country’s top chefs; from amazing locally sourced cuisine in Helsinki, to an expedition in Lapland to learn about foraging and the Finnish delicacy, reindeer!

programme.title: Ireland
programme.desc: It’s the birthplace of Halloween, but the ghosts and ghouls which have canvassed the world have not scared up much interest in Irish cuisine. Mounting a classic motorcycle Jonathan tours a land of mystic traditions, boisterous locals, and iconic scenery. The world’s most magnetic pub culture draws him in, border conflict pushes him out, and dark legends pull him around. It’s an adventure soaked in rain, lore, and the food of ancestor’s past.

programme.title: Frederic Molina – Moulin de Lere
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Taste of France S1 - "Frederic Molina – Moulin de Lere"
programme.desc: At the feet of the Jura mountains,”close to nature” chef Fredric Molina built up an ideal family restaurant and earned his first Michelin star. Let’s explore the secrets to his delicious food, his way of building a power team and how he finds harmony

programme.title: Rene and Maxime Meilleur – La Bouitte
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Taste of France S1 - "Rene and Maxime Meilleur – La Bouitte"
programme.desc: In this program we’ll get acquainted with the unique story of self-taught Rene and Maxime Meilleur, father and son running a three-star Michelin restaurant in Saint-Martin-de-Belleville in the Savoy region.

programme.title: Alexandre Mazzia – AM
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Taste of France S1 - "Alexandre Mazzia – AM"

programme.title: Indonesia - Balinese cuisine: what is it all about?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E09 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Indonesia - Balinese cuisine: what is it all about?"
programme.desc: Balinese cuisine is considered to be extremely complex. Different than what you find in the rest of Indonesia, Bali is further influenced by the major influx of Western tourism. Have the locals kept their traditions and cooking methods strong against the wave of tourism, or have they been catered to suit the palates of foreigners? Liesel heads to the ultimate getaway paradise island, sifts through all the yoga retreats, surfer shacks, and coffee plantations all in an effort to find iconic food - as well as track down the current foodie trend of the island.

programme.title: Ireland - Dublin, what else is there besides the pub culture
programme.sub-title: S01 : E10 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Ireland - Dublin, what else is there besides the pub culture"
programme.desc: Admit it, first thing you relate with Dublin are the pubs. Sure, they are a staple and they serve some of the best brews in the world. And they come with an associated culture that is hard to rival. But what about the food? Does Dublin have a burgeoning foodie scene or is it all about the pint o’ Guiness? Find out on this episode of Max Foodie as Liesel explores the breathtakingly beautiful country of Ireland.

programme.title: Hong Kong - Michelin Madness part 1
programme.sub-title: S02 : E01 Maximum Foodie S2 - "Hong Kong - Michelin Madness part 1"
programme.desc: Big money, big city vibes; Hong Kong houses the world’s highest number of millionaires and it’s something that’s not lost on you as you venture to Asia’s world city. In this episode, Sashi is on a quest to understand how Michelin rates and assesses the sheer depth of eateries in this metropolis. He will meet the top chefs of the city and understand their psyche, their trials and tribulations as they climbed their way to the top of the restaurant industry with 3 Michelin stars. But its not all high brow cuisine, Sashi will also dive deep into the old school neighborhoods, sampling the local fare and seek out how Michelin is rating Asia’s sheer depth of eateries

programme.title: Xishuangbanna Part 1

programme.title: Eric Trochon – Solstice

programme.title: Pascal Barbot - Astrance
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Taste of France S1 - "Pascal Barbot - Astrance"

programme.title: Daniel Barratier – L’Auberge Sur-les-Bois
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Taste of France S1 - "Daniel Barratier – L’Auberge Sur-les-Bois"

programme.title: Philippines - More fun in the Philippines part 1

programme.desc: The story of cacao is more akin to South America, but in this episode, Sashi tracks the story of cacao in the Philippines, the entry point of cacao in Asia. With his friend, Spanish chef, Chele Gonzalez, they embark on an anthropological exploration tracing how the ancestral varietal cacao (crillio) came to be in the Philippine islands. Visiting farms to mystical islands, to top kitchens in Manila, this is the ‘never-before-told’ tale of cacao in the Philippine islands.

programme.title: Philippines - More fun in the Philippines part 2

programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Breaking Beyond S1 - "Goma, Congo"

programme.title: The Ice Hotel V Barbados
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Jet Set S1 - "The Ice Hotel V Barbados"
programme.desc: In freezing temperatures Gill attempts a Jet Set Victory by sculpting her very own ice cat. Unfortunately it leaves Dave feeling rather scared. Richard attempts to heat up the competition from the Caribbean island of Barbados.

programme.title: Chiang Mai V Venice
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Jet Set S1 - "Chiang Mai V Venice"
programme.desc: Richard immerses himself in Thai culture, picking his own rice, learning to cook Thai style with a local top chef and paying a visit to a retired elephant park. While Gill heads to the Italian city of Venice, for a cheeky Bellini in Harry’s Bar.

programme.title: Eze (France) V Stockholm
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Jet Set S1 - "Eze (France) V Stockholm"

programme.title: Amboise (The Loire) and Grenada

programme.title: Venice and Northern Ireland
programme.sub-title: S01 : E12 The Luxury Travel Show S1 - "Venice and Northern Ireland"
programme.desc: This time The Luxury Travel Show visits Venice, one of Europe’s most iconic and enchanting cities as well as Northern Ireland, with a haunted hotel and a trip to where some of HBO’s ‘Games of Thrones’ series was filmed.

programme.title: Barbados and Lake Como
programme.sub-title: S01 : E13 The Luxury Travel Show S1 - "Barbados and Lake Como"
programme.desc: From Barbados to Lake Como this episode is all about fabulous food and famous visitors.

programme.title: Liguria
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Finding Little Italy S1 - "Liguria"
programme.desc: Liguria is more than just a glamorous stretch of Riviera coastline. Giorgio the chef cooks for us and we pop into a local sweet shop; then further still to the towers of Albenga and the postcard views of Cervo.

programme.title: Toscana
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Finding Little Italy S1 - "Toscana"
programme.desc: In this episode we will drive through the UNESCO-protected Val d’Orcia to find a different Tuscany. In lieu of Chianti we will visit the eco-friendly Salcheto winery in the area’s great Montepulciano region.

programme.title: Umbria
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Finding Little Italy S1 - "Umbria"

programme.title: Lesbos, Psara and Chios

programme.title: Chios and Innousses
programme.sub-title: S02 : E07 My Greek Odyssey S2 - "Chios and Innousses"
programme.desc: Peter shows us the sites, sounds and tastes of Chios. Then we cruise north to Inousses, thats been called the cradle of the Greek shipping fortunes.

programme.title: Syros

programme.title: 36 Husbands
programme.desc: 36 Husbands ar en mystisk, musikalisk, Kung Fu-spionkomedi med tre maktiga kvinnor – och ett gang akta man. Toppspionen och Kung Fu-mastaren Krista har speciella krafter och hon anvander dem for att få marschen mot ett tredje varldskrig att gå långsammare.

programme.title: Happy-Go-Lucky
programme.desc: Lararen Poppy anvander sin andlosa optimism for att ta sig genom livets små draman och sprider skratt och gladje till de som finns i narheten.

programme.title: Death At A Funeral
programme.desc: En komisk vriden historia om en dysfunktionell familj som samlas for att sorja sin patriarks bortgång. Daniels far har just avlidit och det enda han vill ar att genomfora begravningen som planerat, vilket inte ar det lattaste med en galen familj på halsen. Brorsan ar mest intresserad av att ragga tjejer, en annan slakting ar overtygad om att fadern ar vid liv i kistan och en mystisk pillerburk dyker standigt upp. Denna dråpliga komedi i brittisk tradition bjuder på många overraskningar.

programme.title: Paper Man
programme.desc: Forfattaren Richard Dunne (JEFF BRIDGES) har en låtsaskompis som foljt honom sedan barnsben: superhjalten Captain Excellent (RYAN REYNOLDS). I ett forsok att återvinna sin forna storhet som forfattare, skickas han ivag till Cape Cod av sin fru Claire (LISA KUDROW) for att skriva sin andra roman. Men då Captain Excellent foljer med som kumpan och hejarklack blir livet dar inte riktigt som planerat... Den 17-åriga flickan Abby (EMMA STONE), vars tragiska forflutna har lett henne till att fly in i sina fantasier, ansluter sig till sallskapet, och en mycket speciell vanskap uppstår.

programme.title: Management
programme.desc: Man kan komma långt på ett glas champagne och en klapp i baken! En frustrerad affarskvinna på forsaljningsresa? Och en misslyckad motelldirektor med smak for billig champagne och runda bakdelar? Ingen vinnarkombination, men mycket kan handa på ett ensligt motell... Hur som helst ar motellchefen Mike snart på vag tvars over USA for att forklara affarskvinnan Sue sin karlek - och forhindra att hon gifter sig med sin mycket beskyddande och inte sarskilt alskvarda fastman!

programme.title: MacGruber
programme.desc: Nar varldsfreden står på spel, nar terroristerna ligger på lur, nar varlden behover en superhjalte med hår som Hillary Clinton... vem kontaktar man då? MacGruber forstås! Enkrigsmaskin utan vapen som kan få ut ALLT av ett gem. En agent så hemlig att inte ensVI kanner till hans fornamn. En man som kvinnor vill vara och som man vill vara tillsammans med... eller ar det tvartom?

programme.title: Neighbor for sale
programme.desc: Nick (WILL FERRELL) har en riktigt dålig dag. Forst får han sparken från jobbet som han haft i 16 år. Nar han kommer hem upptacker han sedan att hans fru har kastat ut hans saker på grasmattan, och bytt lås i dorren. Han har forlorat allt. Detta får Nick att overge sin sex månader långa nykterhet och med olen i handen inratta sitt vardagsrum på grasmattan, dar han fordriver tiden med att titta på grannarna. Nar polisen dyker upp for att mota bort honom, hittar han losningen i ett kryphål i lagen: invånarna i Plano i Texas har ratt att hålla privata loppmarknader i fem dagar i strack.

programme.title: A Haunted House 2

Efter att ha flyttat in i deras dromhem plågas Malcolm återigen av bisarra paranormala handelser, och den har gången ar det inte bara huset som ar hemsokt! Jamie Pressly, Cedric the Entertainer och Essence Atkins medverkar också.

Folj Betty på hennes vilda och hysteriska resa over landet i sokandet efter hennes dromprins. Men kan Betty hitta honom innan mordaren hittar henne?

Calvin (Ice Cube) ar en blivande entreprenor med stora planer... och att driva sin familjs barbershop ar inte en av dem. Men nar han impulsivt saljer butiken till en skum lånehaj inser han snart hur viktig kvartersalongen ar for honom... och hur långt han ar beredd att gå for att få tillbaka den!

Nar det hårda foraldralivet hotar deras mentala halsa och aktenskap så bestammer de sig for att ta med barnen på en resa till Skottland till ett stort slaktkalas och for att halsa på Dougs minst sagt knappa pappa Gordie (Billy Connolly). Det som skulle bli en forsoningsresa forvandlas snabbt till ett hysteriskt roligt socialt katastrofområde nar osamja,

programme.title: The Female Brain

Sofia Vergara och komikern Whitney Cummings har två av huvudrollerna i den har filmen som handlar om vetenskapen bakom våra (ofta beklagliga) romantiska impulser. Den faktaorienterade neuroforskaren Julias forskning om hur den kvinnliga och den manliga hjarnan fungerar illustreras med hjalp av tre olika par i olika faser i deras forhållanden. Men Julias fasta overtygelse utmanas nar en stilig ny forsoksperson deltar i hennes forsok…

programme.title: I Love You Phillip Morris
programme.desc: Steve Russell (Jim Carrey) ar lyckligt gift med Debbie (Leslie Mann) och en monsterinvånare i staden dar de bor. En bilolycka får honom att drastiskt omvardera sitt liv. Steven inser genom en uppenbarelse att han ar gay och beslutar sig for att leva sitt liv fullt ut, aven om det innefattar att bryta mot lagen. Stevens nya syn på livet gor att han ganska snabbt hamnar i fangelset. Dar tar livet annu en ny vandning och han blir galet kar i Phillip Morris, en kanslosam och lågmald kille (Ewan McGregor). Stevens hangivelse att få leva ett liv i frihet tillsammans med Phillip driver Steve till fler och flera innovativa brott.

Båda har sett sina basta dagar, men med hjalp av några okonventionella vanner och en uppmuntrande, men cynisk pappa full av mordande kommentarer kanske de två medelmåttorna kan hitta tillbaka till det som kravs for att vinna over eliten.Med komikerna Jeremy Sisto, Adam Devine och den Oscar® vinnande skådespelaren J.K.

Malcolm hyr in allt från praster till Ghostbusters så att denna demon inte ska få forstora hans forhållande ... eller, annu viktigare, hans sexliv.

Along the way, Carruthers finds himself in more trouble than hed ever expected! Written and directed by Robert N. Bradbury, the film features George Gabby Hayes, Eleanor Hunt, and many other favorites of the era. Wayne was only 27 at the time of Blue Steel, but was well on his way to becoming The Duke.

programme.title: Outpost In Morocco
programme.desc: George Raft, Mary Windsor, and Akim Tamiroff star in this romantic drama from director Robert Florey (The Florentine Dagger, Daughter of Shanghai). Raft plays Capt. Gerard, a member of the Foreign Legion known for his romantic entanglements. Hes assigned to escort an emirs daughter to her fathers mountain citadel and learn about the emirs activities. Not surprisingly, Gerard finds trouble brewing! With footage shot in Morocco, this movie also features a beautiful musical score by twotime Oscar nominee Michel Michelet (Voice in the Wind).

programme.title: Lost Canyon
programme.desc: When Johnny Travers (Jay Kirby) is falsely accused of robbing a bank, its up to Hopalong Cassidy (William Boyd) to clear his name and find the real villains. Theres nothing better than watching Hoppy get rough with the rustlers, and its all the better when you get to hear the Sportsmen Quartette sing (I got Spurs) Jingle, Jangle, Jingle.

programme.title: Wagon Trail
programme.desc: The son of Sheriff Clay Hartley, of the frontier town Elder, has gotten into bad company and hangs out with an outlaw gang in which, Collins, owner of the Golden Rule Saloon, is the secret head. Sheriff Hartley suspects him, but has been unable to gather the needed evidence. Collins instructs his gang, including young Hartley, to hold up the stagecoach on its return trip from Missionary Flats and take the cargo of gold dust it is carrying. Sheriff Hartley is notified of the planned holdup by one of his deputies who has been spying on Collins, and organizes a posse. A deputy-sheriff is killed in the ensuing gunfight between the lawmen and the outlaws, but Deputy Joe Larkin, pursues and...

programme.title: Brothers of the West
programme.desc: Tom Tyler plays Tom Wade, a range detective whose brother has been accused of robbery and murder. Wade has only one clue to prove his brothers innocence: a set of unusual tire tracks. This film was directed by Sam Katzman, who later became known as Jungle Sam for his association with a variety of jungle thrillers, and then as a master of all exploitation genres, from teen horror to flying saucer flicks!

programme.title: Phantom Ranger
programme.desc: Cowboy hero Tim McCoy stars as Tim Hayes, a two-fisted G-Man working for the FBI on a counterfeit money case. The incredibly daring Hayes infiltrates a gang that has kidnapped a Treasury Department engraver. Under the direction of Poverty Row icon Sam Newfield, McCoy turns in another of his legendary slam-bang performances, making Phantom Ranger a perennial favorite of B-Western fans.

programme.title: Fugitive of the Plains
programme.desc: In this continuation of the much loved Billy the Kid serials featuring dreamboat Buster Crabbe (perhaps best known for his numerous appearances as Flash Gordon in the 30s and 40s), Billy finds himself joining an outlaw band led by women in order to, once again, clear his name after being wrongly accused of a crime he did not commit. Helmed by famed B-movie director Sam Newfield, this film also features Al St. John, whose lovable Fuzzy character was as essential to the PRCs Billy the Kid series as Billy himself.

programme.title: Gunsmoke Ranch
programme.desc: Flagg is relocating flood victims to Gunsmoke Ranch. The Three Mesquiteers know Flagg to be a crook and try to warn them. They ignore the warning and improve the land only to find that it has been condemned for a new dam.

programme.title: Neath Canadian Skies
programme.desc: Its the mounties versus claim jumpers in this drama from Golden Gate Pictures. Based on an action-packed novel by James Oliver Curwood and directed by B. Reeves Maynard (Undersea Kingdom, The Phantom Empire), the film features an outstanding cast of Poverty Row regulars, including Russell Hayden, Inez Cooper, Cliff Nazarro, I. Stanford Jolley, and Kermit Maynard. For movie buffs: Cinematographer Marcel Le Picard began his career in the silent era and finished with exactly 200 credits!

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men

programme.desc: A rancher is shot dead after discovering oil on his property. Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This episode aired in 1950.
