programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Recently released from prison, Vic Carver, and his brother Johnny, searches for Annies Uncle Luke to enact revenge. Annie successfully gets her uncle out of town, but an angry Vic kidnaps Tagg. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: With the help of Annie and Lofty, Clay Griffin, a lawman whose eyesight is deteriorating, confronts Johnny Storm and the Murdocks after they are involved in a robbery. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Winter essentials are stolen on their way to a village. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye and Chingachcook suspect that Carpenter is being bamboozled by the Mohawk guide helping him establish a new settlement. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: The son of a neighboring rancher intends to sell their land for a mining operation that will ruin the water rights agreement that Andy and Ben made years ago. Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Days of Jesse James
programme.desc: Famed American western actor and singer Roy Rogers once again plays himself in this Jesse James tale thats a twist on the familiar formula. When he is summoned to bring Jesse to justice after the known villain is suspected of a bank robbery, Rogers soon discovers that Jesse has been framed and that the owner of the bank has robbed his own bank posing as Jesse. Fast-paced and fun, this classic Roy Rogers western directed by Joseph Kane (Dakota) features a whole host of original songs sung by the great Rogers himself.

programme.title: Frontier Justice
programme.desc: Hoot Gibson is back! But he never imagined hed find his father in an insane asylum and his cattle ranch overrun with sheep! Worst of all, Roger Williams stars as the diabolical James WIlton, a rival who isnt above murder. For trivia buffs: Director Robert F. McGowan was the man behind several of the classic Our Gang comedies...

programme.title: Hands Across The Border
programme.desc: Roy Rogers and Trigger star in this Republic Pictures western about horse breeders vying for a contract with the U.S. Army. The cast also includes such favorites as Onslow Stevens and Guinn Big Boy Williams, while songs include Hey Hey (Its a Great Day), Dreaming to Music, and The Girl with the High Button Shoes. For movie buffs: The music for the title song, Hands Across the Border, was composed by none other than Hoagy Carmichael!

programme.title: Colorado
programme.desc: Theres trouble out west! Its the Civil War and the Union needs troops back east to defend itself. Roy Rogers stars as Lieutenant Jerry Burke, who is sent to investigate why the returning troops are being stalled in Colorado. Also starring Gabby Hayes, Pauline Moore, and Milburn Stone, this film is action packed with a turn you wont see coming!

programme.title: Hurricane Horseman
programme.desc: Pancho Gomez kidnaps Don Roberto and his daughter, Tonita for ransom. Can an undercover lawman named Gun Smith save the pair, or will he be caught himself?! Smith gets a job in Gomezs camp supposedly to repair their guns. Instead he fixes the guns so they will misfire. When Gomez refuses to let him go, he sends his horse for the Sheriff! This campy western from 1931 stars Lane Chandler and is sure to keep you enthralled from beginning to end. Directed by Armand Schaefer; starring Marie Quillan and Walter Miller.

programme.title: Way of the West
programme.desc: Government agent Gordon (Hal Taliaferro) goes undercover to investigate an ongoing war between cattlemen and sheepmen. But he soon finds himself framed for murder! This low budget western from the short-lived Empire Pictures is from the golden era of shoot em ups, when audiences knew who the bad guys were, and couldnt wait for the good guys to serve up some just punishment!

programme.title: Hell Town
programme.desc: In Hell Town (aka Born to the West) John Wayne is back in the saddle as two-fisted Dare Rudd, a roaming cowhand trying to prove he can win a womans love and outwit a crooked saloon owner. This exciting B-movie from Paramount Pictures was based on a novel by western writer Zane Grey. With a wild and wooly cast that includes Johnny Mack Brown, Marsha Hunt, Monte Blue, and Lucian Littlefield, director Charles Barton (Abbott and Costello Meet Frankenstein) gives us a tale of romance, action, and high stakes gambling!

programme.title: Range War
programme.desc: William Boyd returns in the 25th of 66 Hopalong Cassidy adventures. This time Hopalong goes undercover to expose a group of ranchers who are interfering with the building of a new railroad. Also, look for Russell Hayden as Lucky Jenkins, and Britt Wood as Speedy McGinnis. Its a great, action-packed adventure from director Leslie Selander (Flight to Mars, Riders of the Range), and further proof that no one pushes Hoppy around and gets away with it!

programme.title: Rage at Dawn
programme.desc: Randolph Scott plays James Barlow, an agent from Chicago hired to bring the notorious Reno brothers to justice. But wouldnt you know it? The Reno gang includes a beautiful young woman (Mala Powers), who catches Barlows eye. This western from director Tim Whelan (The Thief of Bagdad) features cinematography by two-time Oscar winner Ray Rennahan (Gone With The Wind), while the screenplay was by noted author Horace McCoy (They Shoot Horses, Dont They?). Theres also an all-star cast, including Forrest Tucker, J. Carrol Naish, Edgar Buchanan, Denver Pyle, and several other shaggy sidewinders!

programme.title: Valley of Vengeance
programme.desc: LUST FOR GOLD BROUGHT MASSACRE TO HUNDREDS! Death Rode the Plains! Directed by Sam Newfield and starring Buster Crabbe (Flash Gordon) and Al St. John, Valley of Vengeance opens with Billy Carson (Crabbe) shooting two affluential town officials after they - and a band of outlaws - had murdered his and Fuzzys (St. John) parents years earlier. Arrested for the shootings, Billy tells the story of the outlaws killing his parents and the events that led to his shooting the town officials. Will Billy be able to prove his innocence and bring and end to the corrupted officials?

programme.title: Diamond Trail
programme.desc: Diamond Trail is an epic that starts in the speeding taxicabs and illegal barrooms of the east coast, and travels west for its exciting climax. Reporter Speed Morgan (Rex Bell), going undercover as Frisco Eddy, infiltrates Flash Barretts gang in order to bring them all to justice. But can he get the job done before they learn his identity? With a cast that includes Frances Rich and Bud Osborne, this action tale from director Harry L. Fraser (The Last of the Clintons) is another forgotten classic from Monogram Pictures.

programme.title: Fighting Fury
programme.desc: A THRILLING TALE OF REVENGE AND REDEMPTION! Based on the story Triple Cross for Danger by the widely lauded Western author Walter J. Coburn, Fighting Fury is a thrilling take on the Western revenge drama. Portraying both a father and his son, star of silent and sound cowboy adventure films, Jack Hoxie (Trouble Busters, Law and Lawless) exudes the classic American rustic charm that still defines the genre. The film spins the yarn of Clay Hill Jr. (Hoxie), a Spanish-American boy raised by a Mexican servant who vows bloody vengeance on three malicious ranchers after they murder his parents and turn his life upside down. Featuring fine supporting performances from genre heavies Helen Holmes,...

programme.title: The Dude Ranger
programme.desc: Its nothing but action and thrills when an Easterner inherits a cattle ranch and discovers that thousands of cattle have been stolen. Secretly, he signs on as a hired hand at his own ranch to uncover the thief. Once he realizes whats going on, the city boy becomes a hard-riding, avenging son of a six- shooter! Directed by Edward F. Cline from a story by Zane Grey, the film stars George OBrien, Irene Hervey, and LeRoy Mason.

programme.title: Hellgate (Edited Version)
programme.desc: In 1867 Kansas, veterinarian Sterling Hayden treats an injured stranger who turns out to have been a guerrilla raider--and Hayden soon finds himself serving a term in one of the worlds most terrifying prisons under sadistic commandant Ward Bond. Adapted from the story of Dr. Mudd, the physician who attended John Wilkes Booth, assassin of President Lincoln.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat Gallagher and his sidekick Stoney Crockett are Secret Service agents in the Old West, dispatched by the government to investigate crimes threatening the young nation. In this episode, Pat and Stoney are sent to Oklahoma to investigate a hanging judge. Stoneys plan to go undercover backfires when he is framed for murder himself. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat and Stoney are assigned to investigate reports of an impostor posing as a U.S. Secret Service agent operating in Washington territory. In the guise of a government law officer, the man is shutting down all rivals of a saloon keepers operating a crooked gambling establishment. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan. Originally aired in 1952 on NBC.

This episode aired in 1950. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt.

Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.sub-title: S01 : E22 Luck O The Irish
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery. In this episode, Judge Roy and Taggart are intrigued by the arrival of Pat OHara and his much younger wife Kate. Pats fondess for drink and gambling has him involved with the towns rowdies who are eying his beautiful bride. The Judge helps sort things out.

programme.desc: After raising money for charity with a circus sideshow, Annie and Tagg are robbed of their money by a man named the Welshman. Annie and Lofty set up a trap with one last performance. This entertaining western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Tensions rise when a Tuscarawas man tries to incite war against the settlers. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.desc: Hawkeye and Chingachcook help when tensions rise between the Iroquois and the settlers. Hawkeye: John Hart. programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: The Cartwrights take a young boy to the Ponderosa after the death of his mother. Hoss is the only one that is able to get through the boys hostility and bitterness, but, as the two begin to get close, the boys father breaks out of prison and comes to retrieve the boy.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Home in Oklahoma
programme.desc: The entire gang is here! Roy Rogers, Dale Evans, Gabby Hayes, and Trigger are all involved in a murder mystery involving the death of a wealthy ranch owner. Songs include I Wish I Was A Kid Again and Cowboy Ham and Eggs.

programme.title: Lights of Old Santa Fe
programme.desc: Roy Rogers gets involved when his buddy finds himself at odds with a rival rodeo operator. Theres plenty of singing in this musical western, plus enough action to make you realize that Roy Rogers was much more than a singing cowboy! With a cast that includes Dale Evans, George Gabby Hayes, Lloyd Corrigan, and Tom Keene, director Frank McDonald gives us a fun thrill ride through old Santa Fe. Trigger is here, too!

programme.title: The Yellow Rose of Texas
programme.desc: Fans of Roy Rogers and Dale Evans will relish this western adventure. It features no less than nine musical numbers! Songs include, The Timber Trail, Western Wonderland, Lucky Me, Unlucky You, Song of the Rover, and more. Theres even a tune partly written by Cuban bandleader Xavier Cugat! In between songs, theres a plot about a robbery, with Roy playing an insurance investigator trying to solve the riddle of the missing money.

programme.title: Kentucky Rifle
programme.desc: His Wits, Weapons and Women, Turned Defeat Into Victory! A man brings a wagonload of Kentucky rifles through Indian Territory. Unfortunately the Indians realize what he has and offer the travelers an ultimatum: the rifles or their lives! Starring Lance Fuller, Sterling Holloway, Henry Hull, Chill Wills, Cathy Downs, and Jeanne Cagney, plus one of the great B-Western heels, I. Stanford Jolley!

programme.title: Rawhide
programme.desc: Baseball superstar Gehrig is one of several ranchers being coerced by a bunch of bandits. His sister and her lawyer/lover organize the ranchers. Directed by Ray Taylor; starring Smith Ballew, Gehrig, Evelyn Knapp. Talk about stunt casting! Gehrig was a New York Yankees star who was nearing the end of his career, but one of the biggest sports stars in the country. In the movie he plays a variation of himself, as Lou Gehrig, a retired baseball player who takes up ranching. Lou expects to relax on his ranch but quickly joins other ranchers in a fight to protect their properties.

programme.title: Randy Rides Alone
programme.desc: John Wayne was 27 when he starred in this vintage western drama from Hollywoods Poverty Row. He plays Randy Bowers, a man wrongly jailed for murders. With help from a female friend, he breaks out of prison and sets out to find the real killers. Harry L. Fraser (The Last of the Clintons, Rustlers Paradise) directs a strong cast of familiar faces, including legendary sidekick George Gabby Hayes, Earl Dwyer, and one of the hardest ridin stuntmen turned actors, Yakima Canutt.

programme.title: Riders of the Whistling Pines
programme.desc: GENE AUTRY COMES ROARING OUT OF THE SKIES...to save the forests from an outlaw lumber ring! When ex forest ranger Gene tries to interfere with a gang destroying the timberland, hes framed for cattle-poisoning and set up for a murder charge. Yet, he still has time to sing some great cowboy songs, including Its My Lazy Day, and Hair of Gold. This is Gene Autry in a slightly different role, with some great footage filmed at Big Bear Valley and San Bernardino National Forest.

programme.title: The Tall Texan
programme.desc: A group of disparate travelers journey together through the Southwest soon find trouble when they all get gold fever. The action and drama are heightened when they discover gold. The Tall Texan (Lloyd Bridges), is a suspected murderer in the custody of sheriff Lee J. Cobb, and now stranded in Indian territory after a Comanche attack on their stagecoach.

programme.title: Lindell - Sorgmanteln - Del 2
programme.desc: Fyra små flickor på ett fotografi. Tjugo år senare hittas en av dem mordad. En annan ar spårlost forsvunnen. Cato Isaksen ar redo att losa nya kriminalgåtor. Lise Sommer blir upphunnen av sitt forflutna. Hennes basta van Esther Synnøve Lønn har hittats mordad med avskuren hals. Några dagar senare forsvinner Esthers son. Nar polisen borjar att skrapa på ytan visar det sig att en barndomsvan till Lise och Esther Synnøve också saknas. Forhållandet mellan vaninnorna doljer morka understrommar. Vad var det egentligen som hande nar flickorna var små? Och deras mammor - vad doljer de?

programme.title: Tommy
programme.desc: En vecka fore jul landar Estelle Svensson på Arlanda. Ett år tidigare flydde hon hals over huvud med sin dotter och man Tommy som precis genomfort ett av de storsta rånen någonsin i svensk kriminalhistoria. Estelle ar hemma for att hamta Tommys andel av bytet men polisen misstanker att den fore detta gangsterledaren ar dod. Ryktet om Tommys dod sprider sig snabbt i den undre varlden och en dodlig kamp om bytet bryter ut. Nar maktbalansen forskjuts och forna bundsforvanter blir till fiender tar Estelle Tommys plats.

programme.title: Blodsbroder
programme.desc: Efter att ha avtjanat ett långt fangelsestraff ar Jon fast besluten om att lamna sitt kriminella forfl utna bakom sig. Han vill borja plugga och få ett liv utan droger, våld och kriminalitet. Val ute i friheten blir han snart medveten att aven om han avtjanat sitt straff till staten så ar det svårt att helt avskriva skulden till sin omgivning. Av lojalitet till sin yngre bror dras han sakta in i kriminalitetens varld igen samtidigt som han traffar sin stora karlek Marlena.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Varg
programme.desc: Varg ar en storslagen film om Klemens (Peter Stormare) och hans systerson Nejla som lever mitt i det norrlandska landskapet på gransen mellan Sverige och Norge.

programme.title: Helsinki-Napoli All Night Long
programme.desc: Den finske Alex kor taxi på de kalla gatorna i Berlin. Kvallen verkar borja som vilken annan som helst, skjutsa sin fru till jobbet, ta hand om saker med Igor, men sedan hoppar två mystiska man med en stor pengavaska in i bilen, forfoljda av forfoljare! Snart ar skurkarna doda och Alex har i uppdrag att gora sig av med liken.

programme.title: De arvlosa
programme.desc: Mika Kaurismaens forsta långfilm. Han skrev manuset tillsammans med sin bror Aki. "De arvlosa" ar en tidlos skildring av hur småskurken Manne, bonddrangen Harri och den vackra Veera kor en Volga genom de forsvinnande finlandska landskapen, med poliser och gangsters standigt på halarna. Den fartfyllda resan ackompanjeras av tidlosa låtar av bland annat Juice och Rauli Badding.

programme.title: Tatjana
programme.desc: Valto och Reino ger sig av på bilfard och langs vagen plockar de upp Tatjana och Klaudia. Resan går genom ett Finland som inte påverkats av Nokia eller EU utan forblivit urfinskt. Sin vana trogen levererar Kaurismaki en film utan onodig dialog. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Bitchkram
programme.desc: Kristin raknar dagarna till studenten då hon antligen får lamna småstaden och sin manipulativa syster for sina drommars New York. Allt ar perfekt och lokaltidningen på orten har lovat att publicera Kristins kronikor om staden som aldrig sover. Men Kristin missar planet och gommer sig istallet hemma hos Andrea, en marklig ung tjej, långt ute på landet for att undvika total fornedring. I huset ingenstans tar Kristin med Andrea till New Yorks pulserande hjarta i ett vindlande virtuellt aventyr som alla darhemma kan folja i hennes artiklar. Men så tranger sig verkligheten på.

programme.title: Så olika
programme.desc: Så olika ar en komedi om karlek. Det kretsar kring två systrar, den ena nytillsatt finansborgarråd i Stockholm, nyskild och mamma till två dottrar. Den andra en sjalvstandig TV-producent som har fått i uppdrag att gora ett nytt direktsant sångprogram från Skansen - nu mitt bland djuren! Den handlar om att bli sanslost foralskad i sin varsta fiende, om manniskor som mots trots att de ar fundamentalt olika. For har overvinner karleken allt - från politisk maktkamp till dans med salarna på Skansen.

programme.title: Ettor and Nollor - Part 1
programme.desc: FBI och Interpol får nys om en stor kreditkortsharva och pundaren Sebbe plockas in som misstankt. Nar polisen borjar sina forhor får de hora en otrolig historia från Goteborgs undre varld. Svenska och ryska gangsters, marockanska hackers, korrupta politiker och giriga kostymnissar - alla vill tjana stora pengen, ingen vill vara hunden...

programme.title: Ettor and Nollor - Del 2
programme.desc: FBI och Interpol får nys om en stor kreditkortsharva och pundaren Sebbe plockas in som misstankt. Nar polisen borjar sina forhor får de hora en otrolig historia från Goteborgs undre varld. Svenska och ryska gangsters, marockanska hackers, korrupta politiker och giriga kostymnissar - alla vill tjana stora pengen, ingen vill vara hunden...

programme.title: Brott och straff
programme.desc: En filmatisering av Dostojevskijs roman med samma namn, som utspelar sig i 1980-talets Finland. Romanen Brott och straff ar ansedd som en av vår tids storsta litterara verk. Fjodor Dostojevskij målar upp det moraliska dilemmat huruvida ett brott, i det har fallet ett mord ar forsvarbart om resultatet blir positivt for många, om andamålet helgar medlen. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Projekt Z
programme.desc: En grupp filmstudenter tar med sig tre lediga skådespelare till ett nedlagt hotell i de norska fjallen for att spela in en zombiefilm. Deras fiktion blir plotsligt verklighet nar en okand varelse borjar terrorisera filminspelningen.

programme.title: Lindell - Sorgmanteln - Del 1
programme.desc: Fyra små flickor på ett fotografi. Tjugo år senare hittas en av dem mordad. En annan ar spårlost forsvunnen. Cato Isaksen ar redo att losa nya kriminalgåtor. Lise Sommer blir upphunnen av sitt forflutna. Hennes basta van Esther Synnøve Lønn har hittats mordad med avskuren hals. Några dagar senare forsvinner Esthers son. Nar polisen borjar att skrapa på ytan visar det sig att en barndomsvan till Lise och Esther Synnøve också saknas. Forhållandet mellan vaninnorna doljer morka understrommar. Vad var det egentligen som hande nar flickorna var små? Och deras mammor - vad doljer de?

programme.title: Bleeder
programme.desc: Louise alskar Leo djupt, hjartligt och unreservedly och lyckligtvis glad nar hon upptacker hon ar gravid. Men for Leo ar den oforutsedda graviditetsfallet, Det får koppen att stromma over. Barnet betyder ett bestamt farval for hans sista, glittrande hopp att bryta ut ur den sorgliga miljon och bli något.

programme.title: Lindell - Orkestergraven - Del 1
programme.desc: Efter sitt livs basta forestallning på Operan blir forstaviolinisten Siv Ellen Blad brutalt mordad. Kriminalkommissarie Cato Isaksen får snart veta att hon har utsatts for ett postrån. Finns det ett samband?

programme.title: Amazon
programme.desc: Den finske mannen Kari (Kari Vaananen) bestemmer seg for å flytte til Brasil med sine to døtre etter kona hans dør. Snart møter han den eventyrlystne amerikanske flygeren Dan (Robert Davi: Die Hard), som forteller Kari om planen sin om å grave etter gull i Amazonas-jungelen. Men Kari møter også den vakre Paola (Rae Dawn Chong: Commando), som lærer ham mer om situasjonen i Amazonas og truslene mot den.

programme.title: Rosso
programme.desc: Rosso, som skickligt kombinerar roadmovie och kriminaldrama, ar berattelsen om den sicilianska lonnmordaren Giancarlo Rosso, som har kommit till Finland for att leta efter sitt nasta mål, som råkar vara hans alskade Marja. Ovantat får Rosso hjalp med spårningen av Marjas bror Martti, trots att de inte ens delar ett gemensamt språk. På resan ingår både skrotningsuppdrag och några rån...

programme.title: Lognaren
programme.desc: Lognaren ar en beskrivning av en ung skojare som aldrig talar sanning. Den unge mannen spelad av Aki Kaurismaki vandrar genom Helsingfors gator och forsoker låna pengar från bekanta och framlingar med olika forevandningar. Lognaren ar Mika Kaurismakis debutfilm och hans examensarbete från Munchens filmskola.

programme.title: A Polar Year
programme.desc: 28-årige Anders bestammer sig for att resa till Gronland for att undervisa i en liten by. Hans foraldrar tar avstånd från beslutet eftersom de forvantar sig att han ska ta over familjegården, men Anders ser garna ett miljoombyte och nya utmaningar. Livet ar tufft i den lilla byn – tuffare an Anders hade forestallt sig. Byborna tar till en borjan inte emot honom val och om han ska gora sig några forhoppningar om att hjalpa familjerna – inte minst barnen – måste Anders ta ett viktigt beslut. Han måste lara kanna byns manniskor och inte minst deras traditioner. Forst nar han gjort det kommer en helt ny varld att oppna sig for Anders...

programme.title: Mannen utan minne
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om en man som tappar sitt minne och får hjalp av fattiga men storhjartade manniskor i en containerby.

programme.title: Ljus i skymningen (Lights in the Dusk)
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om nattvakten Koistinen som forlorar jobbet, friheten och drommarna. Men till sist skonjer han en strimma hopp.

programme.title: Cha Cha Cha
programme.desc: Den alkoholiserade Matti (Matti Pellonpaa), som bor under broarna, ar på vag att arva en betydande summa pengar från sin amerikanska faster. Men mannen måste vara representativ under fasterns besok. Matti berattar om situationen for sin van som arbetar som bilhandlare, och denne foreslår en rollbyten mot ersattning.

programme.title: De arvlosa
programme.desc: Mika Kaurismaens forsta långfilm. Han skrev manuset tillsammans med sin bror Aki. "De arvlosa" ar en tidlos skildring av hur småskurken Manne, bonddrangen Harri och den vackra Veera kor en Volga genom de forsvinnande finlandska landskapen, med poliser och gangsters standigt på halarna. Den fartfyllda resan ackompanjeras av tidlosa låtar av bland annat Juice och Rauli Badding.

programme.title: Moln på drift
programme.desc: Ilona och Lauri ar ett stravsamt par som inte begar mycket av livet. Tak over huvudet, mat på bordet, ett glas vin och en kvall framfor tv-n. De arbetar plikttroget och agnar sina korta ledigheter åt varandra och sin hund. Men en dag hander något som hotar att slå deras trygga tillvaro i spillror. En varm och absurd historia om ett alldeles vanligt par någonstans i Finland.

programme.title: Kommissarie Spack
programme.desc: Kommissarie Mårten Spack har kallats till en brottsplats dar en kropp hittats genomborrade med knivar, gafflar, skedar och en hogaffel. Till allas forvåning drar Kommissarie Spack slutsatsen att det ror sig om ett sjalvmord. Spack ser kopplingar till andra sjalvmord och konstaterar att kåren fått en galen seriesjalvmordare på halsen. Han kommer snart på andra tankar nar hans råbarkade kollega Grunvald Karlsson hittar andra spår  något som leder till något storre an vad de kunnat ana. En ny kollega, superpolisen Irene Snusk kopplas in på fallet. Tillsammans ska trion losa ett av de viktigaste fallen i svensk kriminalhistoria.

programme.title: I skuggan av varmen
programme.desc: I skuggan av varmen utspelar sig i Stockholm dar två unga manniskor, Eva och Erik, mots och drabbas av den verkligt stora karleken. Eva forsoker forst stå emot karleken - hon har en hemlighet for stor for att kunna tillåta en relation med en annan manniska. I skuggan av varmen ar en karlekshistoria efter Lotta Thells sjalvbiografiska succeroman med samma namn.

programme.title: Layers of Lies
programme.desc: Nar han återvander till Iran efter många år i exil i Finland, finner Sam (Ramin Sohrab) att han annu inte har flytt från sitt forflutna. En skum figur kidnappar hans fru Emma (Jessica Wolff) for att dra in honom i ett våldsamt plan for hamnd. Men Sam ar en obeveklig kampmaskin som inte kommer att stoppa någonting for att radda kvinnan han alskar. Nar det galler att bestamma sin framtid kommer det forflutna inte att stå i vagen for dem... Layer of Lies ar en adrenalinfylld spanningstur genom den livliga, mångsidiga metropolen Teheran.

programme.title: Hotet
programme.desc: Lasse Brudell ar ansvarig programmerare vid flygbasen i Vidsel i Norrbotten. Han arbetar med det topphemliga forsvarssystemet EWS till JAS Gripen. Major Haglund som leder en militar specialstyrka, ar en desillusionerad och arrad krigsveteran. Deras vagar korsas nar Haglund kallas in for att hoja sakerhetsrutinerna infor en demonstration av Gripen for utlandska intressenter. Den eftertraktade mjukvaran ar hårdvaluta i det internationella maktspelet och måste skyddas.

programme.title: Flickan från tandsticksfabriken
programme.desc: Iris ar trott på sitt dodstråkiga jobb och liv. For att pigga upp stamningen beger hon sig ut på stan och shoppar en rod klanning. Natten spenderar hon med en rik man som lamnar henne en summa pengar morgonen efter. En tid senare upptacker Iris att hon ar gravid och upplyser den formogne mannen om sin situation, han skickar en ny bunt sedlar och ber henne att gora abort. Då går Iris ut och koper en stor mangd råttgift.

programme.title: Ariel
programme.desc: Taisto jobbar i en gruva i norra Finland. Nar gruvan stangs reser han mot Helsingfors i en vrakig cabriolet som han ovantat får. Men problemen tornar upp sig. Han blir rånad, hittar inget jobb och doms till fangelse for misshandel. Men med hjalp av sin flickvan Irmeli, en ensamstående mor han traffar i Helsingfors och sin cellkamrat planerar Taisto att bryta sig ur fangelset och starta om på nytt. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Skuggor i paradiset
programme.desc: Nikander ar en ensam sopbils-chauffor som en dag moter den anspråkslosa snabbkopskassorskan Ilona. Nikander blir blixtrande kar, men deras omsesidiga blyghet medfor att det romantiska lyser med sin frånvaro. Så plotsligt andras livet… Ilona får sparken och de bestammer sig for att traffas på ett mysigt litet motell. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Simply Having A Wonderful Xmas!
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Simply Having A Wonderful Xmas!
programme.desc: Feelgood hits and festive favourites from just 1 decade - the 1970s! Santa hat, platform boots and tinsel at the ready?

programme.title: Alternative 80s! with Wayne Hussey
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Alternative 80s! with Wayne Hussey
programme.desc: The Missions gobby frontman with big, bold and ambitious 80s sounds that offered a true alternative to the ever present cheesy pop fare. From Joy Divison in 1980 to Electronic in 89

programme.title: Denises 5*Star Families - Top 30!
programme.desc: Brothers, Sisters, Husbands, Wives - they made it a family business back in the 80s! And Denise Pearson was one of them with her siblings - in pop supergroup Five Star!

programme.title: Monsters of Rock Day!
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Monsters of Rock Day!
programme.desc: Non-stop 80s rock- all day! From Queen, Bon Jovi and Whitesnake to Meat Loaf, U2, The Damned and Billy Idol.

programme.title: The Rock 100 of the 80s
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 The Rock 100 of the 80s
programme.desc: Mark Goodier brings you our exclusive chart of the 100 biggest rock songs of the 80s, based on streaming data, historic sales info, and enduring global appeal. Crank this up LOUD!

programme.title: 50 Wild Women of the 80s!
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 50 Wild Women of the 80s!
programme.desc: Brilliant songs, big voices, blazing hair and bags of attitude - the ladies of the 80s had the lot! From Toyah to Tina and Joan Jett to Janet Jackson.

programme.title: Turbo Trax!
programme.desc: A non-stop ticket to the ultimate retro rave! We crank up the neon and hit the dancefloor with the most electrifying feelgood music videos the 80s had to offer.

programme.title: Kylie! 1988-1989

programme.desc: Nar Joel (Paul Rudd) och Molly (Amy Poehler) mottes var det hat vid forsta ogonkastet: hans storbolag Godiskompaniet hotade att stanga ner hennes bohemiska godisaffar. Plus att Joel fortfarande hade kanslor for sitt sexiga ex (Cobie Smulders). Men, trots allt så blir de kara, tills dess att de gor slut och Molly borjar dejta sin revisor (Ed Helms). Men, precis i sluttampen...tja, du får se helt enkelt. (Ledtråd: Joel håller ett stort tal och de hittar tillbaka till varandra.) Från regissoren som skapade Wet Hot American Summer, Wanderlust och Role Models kommer nu en helknapp och satirisk underminering av den romantiska komedigenren.

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: Youth In Revolt
programme.desc: Michael Cera spelar rollen som Nick Twisp. En unik och alskvard tonåring med smak for livets sofistikerade gladjeamnen, såsom Sinatra och Fellini. På en campingsemester med familjen foralskar han sig i den vackra, intelligenta och frigjorda Sheeni Saunders (Portia Doubleday). Men geografi, familj och svartsjuka ex-partners konspirerar for att hålla Nick och Sheeni åtskilda. Efter uppmuntran från Sheeni overger Nick sitt tråkiga, forutsagbara liv och utvecklar ett rebelliskt alter ego: Francois Dillinger. Med mustasch, slips, djup rost och bad boy-attityd kan inget stoppa Francois från att vara tillsammans med Sheeni.

programme.title: Burning Man
programme.desc: Tom ar chefskock på en chic restaurant på Bondi beach i Sydney. Han ar en arrogant typ som ser flyktigt på tillvaron. Han beter sig sjalviskt och allmant illa mot sina kollegor och sin 8-årige son Oscar, men aven mot de många kvinnorna i hans liv, exfrun Karen, kollegan Sally, psykologen Miriam, Lisa som ar lyckligt gift, prostituerade Lesley och maklaren Carol som skulle salja hans hus. Men Tom har inte alltid varit osympatisk. For tio år sedan traffade han vackra, perfekta Sarah. Hon tog fram det basta hos Tom och gav honom deras gemensamma son.

programme.title: We Too Together
programme.desc: Rob kampar med PTSD efter att ha kommit hem ifrån kriget. Långsamt lar han sig att overvinna sitt forflutna. Under julhelgerna moter han Gabriela som han fullstandigt faller for, och hon alskar honom precis som han ar. Vandning ar total och livet får åter en mening.

programme.title: Bottled with Love
programme.desc: Abbey ar mitt i karriaren, olycklig, frustrerad och hopplost uppgiven efter alla misslyckade dater. Hennes mormor foreslår att hon skriver ner alla hennes onskningar som ett karleksbrev rakt från hjartat. Motvilligt foljer hon rådet och stoppar ner brevet i en flaska och slanger ut den i hamnen. Tiden går och månader senare hamnar Abbey i ett projekt med hennes chefs son Nick. Han ska aven av en handelse hittat flaskan med Abbeys brev, helt ovetande om att det ar hon som skrivit. Sakta borjar Nick forstå kopplingen och får det valdigt jobbigt med situationen och hemligheten. Han beslutar att beratta om det funna brevet. Abbey ber honom dra åt helvete som fort henne bakom ljuset.

programme.title: You Will Meet a Tall Dark Stranger
programme.desc: I denna stormiga komedi av Woody Allen, upptacker två par att graset inte alltid ar gronare på andra sidan. Alfie Shepridge (ANTHONY HOPKINS) dumpar sin fru sedan 40 år (GEMMA JONES), i ett forsok att återuppleva ungdomens nojen tillsammans med en ung callgirl (LUCY PUNCH). For att få ratsida på sitt liv tar den forsmådda hustrun hjalp av en spådam. Samtidigt blir deras dotter Sally (NAOMI WATTS) foralskad i sin chef (ANTONIO BANDERAS), och hennes make (JOSH BROLIN) blir besatt av skonheten som bor på andra sidan gatan (FREIDA PINTO). Och snart hanger både deras forhållanden och deras forstånd i samma skora tråd...

programme.title: Det nast basta (The Next Best Thing)
programme.desc: Yogainstruktoren Abbie och tradgårdsmastaren Robert delar det mesta i livet. Gladje. Sorg. Drommar. Och intresset for killar. Att Robert ar gay ar det enda som hindrar dem från att vara ett par. Sjalvklart festar de också tillsammans, så pass att de efter en helvild natt vaknar upp i varandras armar. De kan bara konstatera att det hant. Och att de gick for långt. På tok for långt. Beviset: ett positivt graviditetstest...

programme.title: You Get Me
programme.desc: Tyler ar vansinnigt kar i sin perfekta flickvan Ali. Nar han efter ett praktgral gor slut med Ali hamnar han i famnen på sexiga Holly. Hon ar ny i stan och ger honom en natt som han aldrig kommer att glomma. Morgonen darpå får Tyler veta att Ali vill ha tillbaka honom och att Holly ska borja på deras skola och hon ar fast besluten att gora Tyler till sin.

programme.title: Love Hurts
programme.desc: Pauls kvinnoaffarer ersatts med flera komiska incidenter nar han måste tillbringa en helg med sina foraldrar, sin fore detta fru och barnen.

programme.title: L.A. Gigolo
programme.desc: Under palmerna i det solbranda Hollywood Hills njuter han av livet som player på stans trendigaste klubbar. Han traffar vackra kvinnor som kan tanka sig att låta en ”Toy Boy” bo i deras hem en kort tid i utbyte mot lite vilt och kravlost sex. Nick har koll på sitt liv och njuter av att vara uppvaktad av den framgångsrika advokaten Samantha (Anne Heche) tills han en dag traffar servitrisen Heather (Margarita Levieva) som spelar samma spel som han sjalv. Hon vill uppåt i varlden och plotsligt måste Nicki inse, att det kravs en del att ”forfora en forforare”.

programme.title: Death of a Ladies Man
programme.desc: En dramakomedi om livet och karleken med låtar av Leonard Cohen från producenterna av ”Brooklyn”, ”Once” och ”Chicago”. Samuel O’Shea ar lyrikprofessor och en levnadsglad kvinnotjusare och entusiastisk alkoholist som har sett battre dagar. Hans andra aktenskap tar slut och hans fru och barn står helt handfallna infor honom. Vad som ar mer oroande ar att han har borjat hallucinera och se saker. Hans valdigt saknade pappa som dog nar Samuel var liten dyker upp for ett snack. Samuel tror forst att det kan vara spriten eller att han kanske bara ar galen eller har for vild fantasi, men får då veta att han har en hjarntumor.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E11 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 11, Romania
programme.desc: Situated in the very heart of the Carpathian Mountains, Sibiu is a Romanian town where the climate is pleasantly mild, offering some of the best weather conditions for a strongman event around Europe. All this, without doubt, set the mood for the high results and showtime vibes in Stage 11 of Strongman Champions League. The competition in Sibiu was organized in six different disciplines

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E12 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 12, Curacao
programme.desc: From now on every stage of these series will be more than crucial. Curacao is a beautiful Dutch island in the Caribbean, with a great atmosphere to hold another stage of the MLO Strongman Champions League. Let’s see who takes the title here and who will secure a place in the next stage.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E13 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 13, Jordan
programme.desc: Ten of the world’s strongest men gathered in Amman to compete in Jordan’s first-ever Truck-Pull Championship. The contestants race against the clock while pulling a 21-ton truck across the track. One of the most fierce competitors to take part in the event was four-time winner of the World’s Strongest Man competition, Brian Shaw.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E14 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 14, Greece
programme.desc: Taking place in Corinth, Greece, considered by many the cradle of the sports competition games, an epic strongman battle will mark the last stage before the upcoming big two-day season’s finale in Chetumal, Mexico. In front of more than 5000 spectators, the twelve athletes compete in Log Lifts, Card Deadlift, Conan’s Wheel and Loading.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E15 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 15, Mexico World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first day of the two-part finale sees the strongest men competing in Carry and Drag, Dumbbell Lift and the Truck Pull. Everything is possible in this heated fight for the crown against the backdrop of stunning Chetumal, Mexico.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E16 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 16, Mexico World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: On the second day of the grand finale of the 2017 Strongman Champions League, the athletes have a last chance to secure the medals in the spectacular four events Weight for Height, Deadlift Cars, Forward Hold and The Loading Medley. Be prepared for stunning performances – and even world records!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E01 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 1, Norway - World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: Season 2018 begins with 14 strongest men in the world, all competing for the title. The competition kicks off in Norway. We’ll see typical Viking disciplines, team events and world records in heavy conditions in the land of snow and ice. They will suffer, they will freeze and fight in this first competition of the year for the title that they will carry on their shoulders throughout whole year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E02 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 2, Germany - FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capichampions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2018 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E03 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 3, Abu Dhabi
programme.desc: For the first time in history, Strongman Champions League will set up competition in Abu Dhabi. The line-up of super athletes, who are part of the SCL, includes former world champions Dainis Zageris (Latvia) and Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland), current world champion Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and biggest strongman in the World Sean O’Hagan (Ireland).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E04 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 4, Holland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Strongman classic in land where there is no place for anything else excepts strength, fight and endurance. Here are fourteen of the strongest men, fighting for the title of strongest in Holland.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E05 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 5, Holland (Part 2)
programme.desc: We go back to Holland, where former champion Dainis Zageris is in leading position after the first three events. Alongside Radzikowski, he is in this moment favorite for world title, and also leader shirt holder.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E06 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 6, Finland
programme.desc: Stage six of Strongman champions league, 2018 is set back on north, in Finland. Here we have Matjaz Belsak, wearing SCL leader shirt, one of the biggest strongman in the World Mika Torro, fan favorite strongman in all over the World – Will Baggott, and also big name from Baltic – Aivars Smaukstelis

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E07 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 7, Serbia
programme.desc: Twelve strongman, including defending Worldchampion Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia , will compete on “Air spa” for the title of best in homeland country of Tesla, Pupin, Novak Djokovic. Matjaz Belsak is the SCL leader in this competition, chasing his third victory this season.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E08 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 8, Finland - U105 (Part 1)
programme.desc: The World championship in lightweights of the Strongman Champions League bring to us 50 strongmen from all over the world. All athletes are under 105 kilograms and for them this is the step up to the ultimate heavyweights.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E09 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 9, Finland - U105 (Part 2)
programme.desc: In this second stage of the World championship of lightweights we will find out who out of the 12 athletes will win the title in the under 105 kilogram category.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E10 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 10, Romania (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of SCL Romania 2018 will be hosted in Brasov. This episode features a new event for Strongman Champion League: “ The Chopper Pull”!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E11 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 11, Romania (Part 2)
programme.desc: After three classical Strongman events – Dead lift, Loading and Front hold – and one historical, Chopper Pull for the first time in history of Strongman, now we go to find out who will take title in Romania. This is the second stage in Romania and it remains to be seen who will win the title; Aivars, Travis or Krzyzstof?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E12 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 12, Curacao (Part 1)
programme.desc: The next destination of Strongman Champions League is in a piece of paradise on earth – Curacao. We bring to you some special Strongman events like the Rock Lift, Tug of War and Weight for Height in this episode.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E13 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 13, Curacao (Part 2)
programme.desc: This is the last competition before the grand finals. After the first three events Zageris is in top place, but can O’Hagan, Baggott, Petursson and Ortmayer step into the final? Last chance some of them will find through events like Forward Hold, Truck Pull, Dead Lift and loading very big objects.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E14 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 14, Road to Mexico
programme.desc: We bring you 50 minutes of Strongman inside. Fears, inspiration, courage, the best and worst from our finalists and their expectation of the finals. We also go to Poland and Germany to represent one day in the training of Krzysztof Radzikowski and Dennis Kohlruss. See all the finalists for Mexico in their comfort zone here, with their backgrounds /motivations /family and friends.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E15 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 15, Mexico - World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of the Strongman Champions League 2018 finals in Mexico. The last twelve athletes all pushing their boundaries and testing their limits to take the World title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E16 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 16, Mexico - World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: After 11 months and 14 competitions all over the world, it all comes down to the final in this episode. The strongmen must show their best skills and every mistake is expensive, so their concentration must be at the highest possible level. Will Krzysztof manage to take off back or will Dainis maintain his lead?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E01 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 1, World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: This year 14 athletes from all over the world came to Fefor to compete in 6 cruel events. Well see typical Viking disciplines on very heavy conditions in land of snow and ice, World records and athletes like the title defender Krzysztof Radzikowski, strongest guys from Holland and Germany and many more

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E02 SCL S6 Ep2 FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capita in the World and of course, the most powerful host in Strongman champions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2019 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E03 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 3, Turkey
programme.desc: On a spectacular beach in Alanya, the MLO Strongman Champions League Turkey was viewed by thousands of spectators over a two day battle. With 12 athletes at the start over 6 cruel events, like Marble Stone Lift, Truckpull and Deadlift cars. And with the comeback of Travis Ortmayer / USA, former stone king and world ranked competitor. Winner of several SCL stages in the past.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E04 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 4, Holland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Four times Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter competing here in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, and 3 in this episode: The first event, a truckpull of 17.000 kg over 25 meters in max 75 seconds, was a real hard pull Also for the World Champion Truckpull, Holland’s runner-up Kelvin de Ruiter, but watch his amazing technique here.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E05 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 5, Holland (Part 2)
programme.desc: Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter, competing in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, 3 in this second episode; a Viking-press of 150 kg with the current world record holder Luke Herrick. The fifth event, a front hold of 25 kg is loved or hated by the athletes and lastly, the Stones of Strength.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E06 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 6, Russia
programme.desc: An unbelievable TANK PULL of 50.000 kg was at the stage of SCL RUSSIA. Never seen this before! Not only a tank pull was done here but also the Viking Press/ Deadlift Max and Log lift reps were spectacular events to see here in Russia. With Mikhail Koklyaev also as event presenter, the former top 3 world strongest man from Russia was there

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E07 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 7, Serbia
programme.desc: In this year’s edition on The Balkan Peninsula, we have competing the new talent from Estonia Marko Remlik together with Sebastian Kurek from Poland and yellow leader Kelvin de Ruiter

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E08 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 8, Finland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Mateusz Kieliszkowski from Poland and Aivars Smaukstelis from Latvia are the strongman future of these days. Mateusz is the best man in the World at the moment to defeat. Only 25 years and such a fantastic strongman. They come here only for a win. But there are 12 more Strong athletes in this episode who want the title of Finland as well.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E09 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 9, Finland (Part 2)
programme.desc: Mateusz Is leading after day 1 (previous episode) with close behind him Aivars Smaukstelis and Zake Muluzi from the UK. All very exciting! 5 events in this episode: Log Lift, Fram Walk, Deadlift, Sack Throw (Weight for Height), Loading medley.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E10 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 10, Portugal
programme.desc: In this stage we have a new strong debutant: Oleg Sylka from the Ukraine. He is the new talent, who will stand up against the old champions like ZSydrunas Savickas and Brian Shaw and the Stoltman Brother from the UK. This new talent Oleg is a great character and we will see him flame in the episode in Portugal.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E11 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 11, Callio
programme.desc: In Callio is the deepest mine of Europe/ 1500 meter deep, whereas the MLO Strongman Champions League also did 1 event. The Forward Hold, on a 1500 dept/ also a kind of new record/ as it was never done before. Spectacular and new in Strongman sport.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E12 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 12, Ukraine
programme.desc: Kelvin de Ruiter is here to defend his SCL World Truck Pull Championships title. But this year, another strong field wants his title. Over 3 different pulls with 3 different trucks, and 14 athletes at the start, it will be difficult for everybody.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E13 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 13, Caribbean
programme.desc: SCL edition Curacao 2019 was a great event, twelve power boys from all over made a great show at the white beaches, and 35 degrees Celsius heat in the Carrabean Islands. Two events were held on Friday at the beach of beautiful resort Sunscape, the other three were held near the world famous floating bridge at Willemstad on Saturday night.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E14 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 14, Dubai
programme.desc: Hosted at Meydan Grandstand in Dubai, the Strongman Champions League had some really big names in the list like Mateusz Kieliszkowski from Poland, Brian Shaw from the USA and Krzysztof Radzikowski. In front of the Burj Khalifa the athletes do the deadlift max and 4 other heavy events at another spot in Dubai.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E15 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 15, World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: With new places on the calendar, over 16 stages, broadcasting in over 100 countries and in its 13th year, the MLO Strongman Champions League (SCL) can be seen truly as the biggest strongman league in the world. The last stage over 2 episodes of the MLO Strongman Champions League, were held in Porto, Portugal. This competition in Portugal is full of memorable performances and strong results.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E16 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 16, World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: With new places on the calendar, over 16 stages, broadcasting in over 100 countries and in its 13th year, the MLO Strongman Champions League (SCL) can be seen truly as the biggest strongman league in the world. This competition in Portugal is full of memorable performances and strong results and this is the final!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E01 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 1, Norway
programme.desc: The spectacular Fefor Arena hosted for the 8th time the Worlds Strongest Viking, part of the SCL World Series. But with the absence of former title holders its anyones game. Again, a very spectacular episode of the Strongman Champions League here in Norway.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E02 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 2, Finland (Part 1)
programme.desc: In this episode, the Titan, former double World champion from Latvia will compete against his fellow countryman and the current World champion - Aivars Smaukstelis. With 8 events over 2 stages the contestants are pushed to their limits in Finland.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E03 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 3, Finland (Part 2)
programme.desc: Dainis Zageris and Aivars Smaukstelis, both from Latvia have a serious, strong battle in the this second and final episode of the SCL Finland 2020. Watch the unbelievable and brute power of these athletes in the last 4 events to crown the winner.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E04 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 4, World Record Breakers
programme.desc: The SCL Germany event takes place in an ancient castle called Die Burg in the heart of Germany. Its here where 5 world record attempts take place across 5 different events with 10 athletes. They will go to the max! See this and much more in the SCL Germany 2020.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E05 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 5, Strongest Viking
programme.desc: SCL Norway is normally all about snow, wind, and cold weather. Our brave athletes are used to compete under conditions few other athletes have competed in, but after COVID delays the competition has been moved from winter to summer bringing in a whole new range of challenges. With an impressive athlete list who will be the winner across 5 cruel events?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E06 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 6, World Strongest Team 1
programme.desc: Were in sunny Finland for the next stage of a double-bill of SCL action, but this time its a team event. A truly fantastic event with 6000 spectators. Even during COVID times this was exceptional! 8 Strong Teams where fighting for the title over a crazy 9 events.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E07 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 7, World Strongest Team 2
programme.desc: Day 2 of the famous Team World championship here in Finland, done over 9 cruel events. In this episode the last and final 5 events take place. 8 Strong Teams are fighting for the title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E08 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 8, Portugal
programme.desc: The next set of challenges are set in sunny Esposende in Portugal. With stars such as Travis Ortmayer, Kelvin de Ruiter from Holland, and Ervin Toots from Estonia. While Fabio Silva will defend the honour in his own country.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E09 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 9, World Records (Part 1)
programme.desc: We are back in Germany, with the world record breakers. We promise you this is going to be amazing. Do not move from that seat, because we are going to see some records smashed today. Over 6 cruel events, you will see who gets crowned of the King Of The Castle!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E10 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 10, World Records (Part 2)
programme.desc: With the next episode of Strongman Champions League Germany. Its the world record breakers, and in the last show we set two new records. Can more be records be broken before the king of the castle is crowned?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E11 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 11, Worlds 105 Kg (Part 1)
programme.desc: Welcome to Kokkola in Finland. This city will be the setting for the Lightweight World championship. Out of 24 athletes, only 16 will make it through to the final day, but who will champion each event and who is going to be eliminated?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E12 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 12, Worlds 105 Kg (Part 2)
programme.desc: Its the second day, and the top 16 athletes have made it through to the final round. With another 4 events to go who will get the crown of world champion?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E13 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 13, Ukraine
programme.desc: Welcome to Ukraine and the wonderful capital city of Kyiv. Were here for the second time for the iconic truck pull World Championships! The reigning World champion Kelvin de Ruiter from Holland will defend his title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E14 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 14, Romania
programme.desc: In this episode, a final chance for our athletes to get vital world series ranking points on board to give them the best possible chance of success and an initial advantage at the finals. Its the last show before the world finals and the top 10 places are up for grabs, but who will they be?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E15 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 15, World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: We are in Alanya, on Turkeys south-coast for the final stop at the end of a mammoth season. Here in the sunshine, well finally crown our world champion and what a place Alanya is - you could not ask for a better setting. Aivars Smaukstellis, the reigning world champion is defending his title, and two-time world champion Dainis Zageris is also here, but with a though competition, who will win?

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Top Million Dollar Agent

Daryl knows all about tranquility and goes golfing with Mike to discuss his client and Mikes listing for them.

programme.title: Henrys Crime
programme.desc: Henry ar en man utan ambitioner i livet. Men då han tar på sig skulden for ett rån han inte begått, kommer han till insikt om sitt ratta kall. Tillsammans med sin cellkamrat Max bestammer han sig for att iscensatta en spektakular bankkupp. Och sen moter han Julie, en alldeles bedårande teaterdiva, vilket leder till en hel del ovantade problem.

programme.title: Twin Peaks: Fire Walk with Me
programme.desc: En kropp fardas med floden, insvept i plast, i den lilla staden Deer Meadow, Washington. FBI kopplas in, men mitt i utredningen forsvinner ena agenten spårlost. Han ersatts av den intuitive Special Agent Dale Cooper, som kanner på sig att mordaren kommer upprepa sitt brott. Ett år senare, i Twin Peaks, lever Laura Palmer ett sjalvdestruktivt liv till foljd av sin barndoms trauman. Så dyker mordaren upp igen. Twin Peaks: Fire Walk with Me ar långfilmen som knot ihop de losa trådarna efter den kultforklarade tv-serien, genom att beratta handelserna som foregick serien.

programme.title: Flickan från tandsticksfabriken
programme.desc: Iris ar trott på sitt dodstråkiga jobb och liv. For att pigga upp stamningen beger hon sig ut på stan och shoppar en rod klanning. Natten spenderar hon med en rik man som lamnar henne en summa pengar morgonen efter. En tid senare upptacker Iris att hon ar gravid och upplyser den formogne mannen om sin situation, han skickar en ny bunt sedlar och ber henne att gora abort. Då går Iris ut och koper en stor mangd råttgift.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: 200 Cigarettes
programme.desc: Det ar nyårsafton i New York, år 1981. Monica ska ha fest, men vid niotiden har ingen dykt upp. Hennes gaster ar på vag, men de har inte bråttom. Kevin har ingen lust att fira nyår eftersom han nyligen blivit dumpad. Val och Stephie går vilse och hamnar på en klubb. Bridget och Caitlyn forsoker bli av med Bridgets pojkvan Eric. Alla ar de på jakt efter sex, karlek eller båda två.

programme.title: Man About Town
programme.desc: Jack Giamoro ar den amerikanska drommen forkroppsligad. Som Hollywoods mest efterfrågade talangscout tillhor han filmstadens absoluta gradda. Snabba bilar, valfyllda bankkonton och en vacker hustru - you name it, Jacks got it. Men nar han på en och samma dag forlorar sin dagbok - som ar full med konfidentiellt Hollywood-skvaller - och avslojar hustruns snedsprång, dalar Jacks tillvaro från "bling-bling" till absolut ingenting. Och så borjar guldfiskens desperata kamp for overlevnad i ett hav fullt med hajar.

programme.title: Seeking a Friend for the End of the World
programme.desc: Nar en asteroid narmar sig jorden blir en man (Steve Carell) ensam efter att hans hustru lamnat honom i panik. Han bestammer sig for att ta en "road trip" for att återforenas med sin high school sweetheart. Grannen (Keira Knightley) foljer med honom for att oavsiktligt satta kappar i hjulet for hans plan.

programme.title: Cypher
programme.desc: I ett skuggigt rike av foretagsspionage, snubblar en uttråkad alla in i ett nat av bedrageri och blir en omedveten spion. Nar han navigerar i forraderi och svek, samarbetar han med en forforisk gåta for att avsloja chockerande sanningar och återta sin identitet.

programme.title: Secrets and Lies
programme.desc: Eftersom Hortense ar svart blir hon forstås forundrad nar hon får reda på att hennes biologiska mor ar en vit arbetarklasskvinna på vag allt langre ut i den samhalleliga periferin. Upptackten av sin nya familj forandrar Hortense, och att låta sig involveras i deras liv forandrar hennes likaval.

programme.title: Hollywoods hemlighet
programme.desc: 1924 samlade mediamogulen William Randolph Hearst några av varldens mest kanda personligheter for en resa med sin yacht som resulterade i ett mord som forblev olost.
En ung forfattare tvingas att acceptera sin dodlighet nar han diagnoseras med en sallsynt form av cancer. Med hjalp av sin basta van och en ung terapeut finner han modet att mota sjukdomen.

programme.title: Hercules I New York
programme.desc: Forvisad från Mount Olympus skickas Hercules, (Arnold Schwarzenegger), till jorden dar han hittar sann karlek och borjar en lovande karriar som kroppsbyggare.

programme.title: Det låsta rummet
programme.desc: Sean och Derek ar två småtjuvar specialiserade på att ta anstallning på restaurangparkeringar, med syfte att lansa rika gasters hem medan de ar borta. Under inbrottet hos den formogne Cale Erendreich finner Sean en hemlig dorr som han dyrkar upp. Skrackslaget får han nu bevittna en illa skadad kvinna fastspand i en tortyrstol. I panik flyr han for att kontakta polisen, men nar de anlander finns inga spår av offret. Plågad av insikten att Sean lamnade kvinnan i sticket tvingas han och Derek att sjalva undersoka fallet, men Cale vet vilka de ar…

programme.title: Awake
programme.desc: En man vaknar på sjukhuset utan att minnas vem han ar och hur han har hamnat dar. Hans sjukskoterska (Eastwood) hittar ingen legitimation på honom och kallar honom bara John Doe (Rhys Meyers). Polisen brakar in på sjukhuset och anklagar John for att vara en seriemordare som har dodat flera unga kvinnor i trakten. Nar John ska foras till forhor lyckas han fly med hjalp av Diana, som ar saker på att han ar oskyldig. De kor till den senaste brottsplatsen for att hitta ledtrådar och svar som kan rentvå John från misstankarna. Den snalla sjukskoterskan tar reda på den skakande sanningen om Johns identitet och det nat av logner och svek som slutar i en sista kamp om hans overlevnad.

programme.title: Twin Peaks: Fire Walk with Me
programme.desc: En kropp fardas med floden, insvept i plast, i den lilla staden Deer Meadow, Washington. FBI kopplas in, men mitt i utredningen forsvinner ena agenten spårlost. Han ersatts av den intuitive Special Agent Dale Cooper, som kanner på sig att mordaren kommer upprepa sitt brott. programme.title: Foralskad I Rom
programme.desc: Woody Allen fortsatter sin filmiska resa genom Europas huvudstader. I Rom har allt och alla sin egen historia. Rom ar staden dar manniskor mots och dar alla kan hitta sitt eget aventyr. Vi får bland annat folja Hayle, en ung amerikanska på semester som moter den vackre Michelangelo med en minst sagt udda familj, nygifta Antonio och Milly från italienska landsbygden som kommer på brollopsresa till Rom, den beromde arkitekten och så den till synes helt obetydlige Leopoldo Pisanello vars enformiga liv plotsligt en dag drastiskt forandras.

programme.title: Death At A Funeral
programme.desc: En komisk vriden historia om en dysfunktionell familj som samlas for att sorja sin patriarks bortgång. Daniels far har just avlidit och det enda han vill ar att genomfora begravningen som planerat, vilket inte ar det lattaste med en galen familj på halsen. Brorsan ar mest intresserad av att ragga tjejer, en annan slakting ar overtygad om att fadern ar vid liv i kistan och en mystisk pillerburk dyker standigt upp. Denna dråpliga komedi i brittisk tradition bjuder på många overraskningar.

programme.title: Youre Not You
programme.desc: Dubbelt Oscar-belonade Hillary Swank spelar huvudrollen som den framgångsrika konsertpianisten Kate som drabbas av den obotliga sjukdomen ALS. Hennes familj erbjuder henne de basta tankbara vårdarna, men Kate sjalv faller for den oborstade och helt inkompetenta Bec. Och med en lakande kur bestående av lika delar skratt och tårar hittar de två helt vasensskilda kvinnorna vagen in till varandras starka sidor.

programme.title: Rabbit-Proof Fence
programme.desc: Tre piger – halvt hvide, halvt aboriginere – skal skoles til at arbejde for hvide familier og derefter havne i en sammenhæng, hvor de med tiden kan gifte sig med hvide mænd. Men pigerne beslutter at flygte, og de følger det over 1500 kilometer lange hegn langs statsgrænsen på et omvæltende eventyr i den australske vildmark.

programme.title: The Dresser
programme.desc: En odesdiger natt på en liten engelsk teater under andra varldskriget, satter en trupp med kringresande skådespelare upp Shakespeares "King Lear".

programme.title: 200 Cigarettes
programme.desc: Det ar nyårsafton i New York, år 1981. Monica ska ha fest, men vid niotiden har ingen dykt upp. Hennes gaster ar på vag, men de har inte bråttom. Kevin har ingen lust att fira nyår eftersom han nyligen blivit dumpad. Val och Stephie går vilse och hamnar på en klubb. Bridget och Caitlyn forsoker bli av med Bridgets pojkvan Eric. Alla ar de på jakt efter sex, karlek eller båda två.

programme.title: Saints Of War
programme.desc: Jersey, 1942. Hitler starker sitt grepp om Vasteuropa och Kanaloarna blir ockuperade. Tyskarna anvander Jersey som en bas dar krigsfångar slavarbetar i arbetslager och Jerseys invånare står infor en osaker framtid med radsla som frestar på humor och testar lojaliteter bland de tatt sammansvetsade i ons samhalle.

programme.title: Time Out of Mind
programme.desc: George ar en desperat man. Med en vacklande halsa och ingenstans att ta vagen hamnar han på New Yorks obarmhartiga gator. Efter trostlosa forsok att hitta en tillfallig bostad tar han sin tillflykt till Bellevue Hospital, Manhattans storsta center for hemlosa man. Även har ar det en hård och tuff miljo, full av utstotta sjalar. Men nar George blir van med Dixon, en arrad hemlos man, infinner sig hoppet om att kunna reparera sitt dåliga forhållande till sin dotter.

programme.title: Cypher
programme.desc: I ett skuggigt rike av foretagsspionage, snubblar en uttråkad alla in i ett nat av bedrageri och blir en omedveten spion. Nar han navigerar i forraderi och svek, samarbetar han med en forforisk gåta for att avsloja chockerande sanningar och återta sin identitet.

programme.title: Jungle
programme.desc: Den unge, israeliske Yossi Ghinsberg lamnar en trygg framtid bakom sig for folja en osannolik drom som for honom in i Amazonas regnskogs mystiska djup.. Under ett års tid gor han en resa som många innan honom har gjort men nar han blir bekant med två andra aventyrare, Kevin Gale och Marcus Stamm och de tre moter den morka och karismatiske Karl Ruchprecter foljer de med honom in i djungeln. Vad som borjar som forverkligandet av en drom forvandlas snart till ett hemskt och psykologiskt test av fortroende och mod. Den sanna historien om att overleva mot alla odds, baserad på Yossi Ghinsbergs memoarer.

programme.title: Lost Highway
programme.desc: Fred Madison och hans fru Renee hittar mystiska videoband på verandan, på banden syns deras hus. Forst filmat utifrån. På nasta, inifrån. Polisen ar inte intresserade av att hjalpa paret, men nar annu ett videoband dyker upp och visar Renees dod vacks i stallet misstankarna mot Fred. Och darifrån ska ingenting komma att bli mindre mardromslikt. Lost Highway ar en neonoirthriller av en David Lynch i hogform, med Bill Pullman (Independence Day) och Oscarsbelonade Patricia Arquette (Boyhood) i huvudrollerna.

programme.title: Walking Tall
programme.desc: Nar det galler att skipa lag och ratt kan en man gora skillnad! Actionstjarnan Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson tar inga fångar nar han kampar for rattvisa och krossar korruption i denna berattelse om en man som tar stallning… och tar tillbaka sin stad!

programme.title: My Week With Marilyn
programme.desc: I ett desperat forsok att bli tagen på storre allvar reser ikonen Marilyn Monroe (Michelle Williams) till London 1956 for att spela mot legenden Laurence Olivier i “Prinsen och balettflickan”. Den omhetstorstande Marilyn kanner sig overgiven av maken Arthur Miller och attraherad av Oliviers assistent, den unge Colin Clark. Colin blir snart Marilyns fasta och trygga punkt, samtidigt som han också blir Oliviers endahopp att kunna slutfora sin film genom sin formåga att hålla den impulsiva Marilyn i schakt. Upp over oronen foralskadar det nu Colins hjarta som riskerar att krossas av varldens storsta och vackraste filmstjarna!

programme.title: Quest
programme.desc: Bengal has not only been home to the former capital of British India but also been the land where many European colonies vied for dominance and cultural supremacy. As a result, the cuisine of the land underwent a renaissance, wherein it imbibed many European influences including Portuguese, Dutch and Danish. Alex visits what used to be a Danish settlement on the banks of the river Hooghly, and she unearths recipes, which were born from this delicious amalgamation of cultures.

programme.title: Xplore Bhutan
programme.desc: Known as Druk Yul or the “Land of the Thunder Dragon”, Bhutan is the country of mountains, monasteries and mystery. Radhika Bangia finds this to be true when she visits Punakha, the former capital of Bhutan, where she marvels at the architecture of Punakha Dzong and gets to know the story behind the two rivers, Mo Chhu and Po Chhu. She also explores the sacred temples and Mebar Tsho lake of Bumthang, the religious heart of Bhutan, and gets to know the local legends.

programme.title: World Spas

programme.title: 10 Days Scotland
programme.desc: Robbie’s journey to reconnect with his Scottish roots begins in Edinburgh, the stunning capital city perched on extinct volcanoes. Navigating the twists of the Royal Mile, strutting around the majestic Edinburgh castle and learning to sip scotch like a true Scotsman, he feels a tad closer to his heritage. The real fun kicks in, however, when he stumbles onto a rather flamboyant way to unleash his inner Highlander.

programme.title: Xplore Bulgaria
programme.desc: Like Rome, Plovdiv straddles seven hills; but as Europe’s oldest continuously inhabited city, it’s far more ancient. As Catriona takes a tour of the city to see its iconic attractions such as a Roman Amphitheatre, which was once the setting for gladiator fights, and the striking Baroque Saints Constantine and Helena Church, she begins to see how seamlessly modern life blends with the age-old ruins. Along the way, she realizes why Plovdiv is called the ‘Eternal City’ of Bulgaria.

programme.title: 10 Days Scotland
programme.desc: Robbie’s journey to reconnect with his Scottish roots begins in Edinburgh, the stunning capital city perched on extinct volcanoes. Navigating the twists of the Royal Mile, strutting around the majestic Edinburgh castle and learning to sip scotch like a true Scotsman, he feels a tad closer to his heritage. The real fun kicks in, however, when he stumbles onto a rather flamboyant way to unleash his inner Highlander.

programme.title: Xplore Bulgaria
programme.desc: Like Rome, Plovdiv straddles seven hills; but as Europe’s oldest continuously inhabited city, it’s far more ancient. As Catriona takes a tour of the city to see its iconic attractions such as a Roman Amphitheatre, which was once the setting for gladiator fights, and the striking Baroque Saints Constantine and Helena Church, she begins to see how seamlessly modern life blends with the age-old ruins. Along the way, she realizes why Plovdiv is called the ‘Eternal City’ of Bulgaria.

programme.title: Angry Planet
programme.desc: Filming the volcanoes, mudpools and geysers in the geothermic wonderland of New Zealand’s north island, we learn that a new island is being created by an undersea volcano 1000 miles north in Tonga. Determined to be among the first to see this “newest land on earth”, we head for the remote island by plane and boat, after various nautical mishaps, George ends up, bedraggled and clad in nothing but underwear and a lifejacket, honored to be one of the very first to explore this brand new island.

programme.title: Angry Planet
programme.desc: In 2000, a remarkable find was made in Chihuahua, Mexico, of a spectacular cave filled with giant crystals, some over 20 meters long. But it is a intensely difficult spot to explore – with temperatures over 50 degrees C and humidity well over 100%. George leads an Explorers Club Flag Expedition into the cave, wearing special refrigerated suits and respirators to battle the extreme environment.

programme.title: Angry Planet
programme.desc: We break the bounds of earth, and look at the environment of space. We examine the difficulties and challenges of exploring this most challenging environment.↵ ↵George experiences some of the extreme training needed for space travel –aboard a Czech-built Albatross fighter jet, the Zero-G plane, and a centrifuge producing 6 G’s of force, and witnesses the launch of a flight to the International Space Station.

programme.title: Angry Planet
programme.desc: George links up with two experienced polar adventurers to explore the frigid Canadian arctic in the depths of winter. The team first uses skis to cross the fractured sea ice of Frobisher Bay, then dog teams to head north through the spectacular Auyuittuq Mountains.

programme.title: Angry Planet
programme.desc: The “Angry Planet” team hopes to film the natural wonders and extreme phenomena of this fascinating Central Asian country, including a spectacularly burning crater of natural gas, underground lakes, sandstorms and remnants of the dinosaurs.

programme.title: Sweets on the menu
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Julies Frenchy Cookbook - Season 4 - Sweets on the menu
programme.desc: Today, Julie takes us down a different kind of yellow-brick road, one that tastes of childhood and gourmet delights: the road of sweets. France may be famous for its gastronomy, but its not to be outdone when it comes to pastries and confectionery - quite the opposite. “Betises” from Cambrai, "Berlingots” from Carpentras, "Calissons” from Aix-en-provence, every region in France has its own sweet or confectionery.

She then attends a perilous acrobatic yoga class with Vibe Yoga where her sense of balance has been challenged a few times. Believe or leave! This is Bol Meditation’s motto where Val discovers the benefits of Intense meditation on our body and mind. All together, this place is a piece of heaven in the middle of ettic L.A.

programme.title: Chromo Yoga and Detox Juices with Mia Frye
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen Trendy - Season 2 - Chromo Yoga and Detox Juices with Mia Frye
programme.desc: Val will make us discover Chromo Yoga, which combines light and color therapy with yoga.
